Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.29,0:40:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}惊恐  售罄
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.88,0:42:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}午夜来见  别说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.49,0:43:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}上帝保佑国王
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.42,1:33:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}维奥莱特  我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:00:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为主献身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...serve the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为圣灵的力量欢喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}rejoicing in the power of his Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全能的主赐福你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the blessing of God Almighty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣父圣子圣灵保佑你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit be upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远与你们同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and remain with you all forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了  看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're coming. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦大家看这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you could all look this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过这样的婚礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have never seen a wedding like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可比我们的气派多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a bit grander than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可还没道喜呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't noticed any congratulations on your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逗他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't tease him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祝福那小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish the boy well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帅气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-玛丽  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ah, Mary. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亲爱的  你看到蛋糕了吗  -太好看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Darling, have you seen the cake? - It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就住这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're going to live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去老宅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm off to the dower house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到能暖和地度过冬天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The thought of being warm in winter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像喝了烈酒一样上头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}goes to my head like strong drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不难想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要切蛋糕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to cut the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想感谢你让我能如此幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to thank you for allowing me to be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己真是三生有幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like I've been given much more than I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好开端嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's an encouraging start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  蛋糕真大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Splendid. Size of that cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再见  -给我们寄明信片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Goodbye. - Send us a postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你们做的一切  -再见  老伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you for everything. - Bye, old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再见  -蜜月愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bye-bye. - Have a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一路顺风  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have a safe journey. - We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了莫里先生的来信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've had a letter from Mr. Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他周二要来唐顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's coming to Downton on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-您找他干什么  -不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you want him for? - Oh, it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你奶奶把他叫来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was your grandmother who summoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他希望我们也在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd like us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯孟德  你也该在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rosamund, you should be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天啊  -这什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, dear. - Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太太叫律师只有一个原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's only one reason old ladies summon their lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs16\bord0\fn微软雅黑\b0\pos(374,247)}希腊神话\N得罪神明的埃塞俄比亚公主被锁链绑在了岩石上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这么围着我  我觉得像被栓在石头上的{\u1}安德洛墨达{\u0}\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like {\u1}Andromeda{\u0} chained to a rock with you lot hovering over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道莫里为什么没问过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why Murray told you to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫你们也来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without asking me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nor do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, Denker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有位莫里先生快要到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Mr. Murray will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经到了  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}H-He's here now, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他跟您约好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He... he says you're expecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  那你怎么不告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该这么疑神疑鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be so untrusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您已经告诉他们了吗  老夫人  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you told them, Lady Grantham? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她什么都没跟我们说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's told us nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's easily done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了一栋位于法国南部的别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've come into possession of a villa in the south of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要把它送给我的曾孙女茜玻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now I've given it to my great-granddaughter Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪点没听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What bit didn't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么别墅  在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What villa? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议到让人无言以对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is too extraordinary for any words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫鸽子别墅  在土伦附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's called La Villa des Colombes, and it's near Toulon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么会属于您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But why was it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且您怎么从没提过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why have you never said anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我以为那是个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I thought it was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从头说起吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年前  你出生之前  我去了趟法国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Years ago, before you were born, I was in France,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到了一个男人  蒙米拉侯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I met a man, the Marquis de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邀请我去他刚买的一栋别墅做客几日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he invited me to spend some time at a villa he'd just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概一年多后  他写信给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A year or so later, he wrote to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他已把别墅转到了我名下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and said he'd transferred the villa into my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没想到他是认真的  我没在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never thought he was serious, so I didn't pay any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但并不是玩笑话吗  -看来不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But it wasn't a joke? - It seems not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最近过世了  让他的遗孀惊讶的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He died recently, and to his widow's alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们多年来每年冬天都去住的别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the villa they've been using every winter for years
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是在老夫人名下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was registered to Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直没改过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要几个签名  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Now, I'll need some signatures. - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为什么要送给茜玻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why have you given it to Sybbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的孩子在这里有财产可继承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your children are well set up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊迪丝的孩子更是不愁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Edith's are more than taken care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但布朗普顿会由汤姆和露西的孩子继承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Brompton will go to a child of Tom and Lucy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样亲爱的茜玻的独女就继承不到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So darling Sybil's only daughter will inherit little,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改变这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I wanted to correct that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个蒙米拉有多少家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What family did he have, uh, this M-Montmirail chap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗孀和一个儿子  也就是现任侯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The widow and a son, the present marquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位母亲很想把此事闹上法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother is keen they should take the matter to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这也难怪  -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, you can't blame her. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她丈夫想把房子送给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If her husband wanted me to have the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们凭什么说不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who are we to argue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就没想过要拒绝吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never thought to turn it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像是会拒绝一栋南法别墅的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I look as if I'd turn down a villa in the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫里先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以帮我个忙吗  -请讲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- May I ask a favor? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个任务交给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信里都说明了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all explained in this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过几日再发电报  以防还有什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll telephone in a few days in case there are questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  格兰瑟姆夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要赶不上车了  -再见  莫里先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Now, I hear my train calling. - Goodbye, Mr. Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想让我说出他为什么这么干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to tell you why he did it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就此道晚安了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with that, I will say good night
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们议论我的神秘过往去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and leave you to discuss my mysterious past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹可  别推推拉拉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Denker, don't steer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是赛车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a racing car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More's the pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really must try...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是挺奇怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does seem odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们60多年前在一个度假山庄一起待了几日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They spend a few days together in the same resort more than 60 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就送了她栋房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he gives her a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该不会只是个疯子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose he wasn't just a lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会想证明他是疯了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's what they'll try to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得奶奶这样照顾茜玻真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I think it's marvelous of Granny to take care of Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕蒙米拉先生真是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if Monsieur de Montmirail was as mad as a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妈妈为什么从没提起过呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But why did Mama never say a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她看来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As far as she's concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她半个多世纪前收到了一封古怪的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she received a very eccentric letter more than half a century ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时以为只是胡闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she considered it potty at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再没去想过这事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and never gave it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  玛丽戈德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Marigold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  打得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right. Good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保姆  看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nanny, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话找您  老爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A telephone call for you, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是谁  -一位巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who is it? - Uh, a Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-说是英国雄狮的  -那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Says he's from British Lion. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一家电影公司吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a film company, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好去看看是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I better find out what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们夏季打算怎么处置别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will they do with the villa in the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不能租出去  没人那时候去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't let it. Nobody goes there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-现在有人去了  -难道不热吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, they do now. - Well, surely it's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是不热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-妈妈  -你好  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mummy! - Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  来玩吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy, come and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比赛呢  来  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a race. Come on. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴伯先生是一位制片人和导演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Barber turns out to be a producer and director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想在这里进行连续摄影术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wanted to practice chronophotography here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又不是石器时代  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the Stone Age, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说他想在唐顿拍电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean he wants to make a film at Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我委婉地拒绝了  -那我再打回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I let him down gently. - Then I'll ring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听听他的提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to hear what he has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会给钱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I suppose there'd be a fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利什么时候回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When does Henry get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶不上这事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not in time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他人在哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最后是从伊斯坦布尔还是什么地方来的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His last message was from Istanbul or somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我看来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as far as I'm concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么汽车拉力赛真是发疯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the whole idea of a rally is barmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有他你也能行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can manage it without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那么就都靠我了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see. So it's down to me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能指望我们去应付演艺人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't expect us to deal with kinema people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先听听他的提议吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First, let's just listen to his proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  玛丽  我陪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come along, Mary. I'll keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱总能派上用场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The money would be useful, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟亨利一切都好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is everything all right with Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爱车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in love with cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他爱速度  他爱冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in love with speed. He's in love with adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像还爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's also in love with me, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我似乎无法抵消另外三样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't seem to cancel out the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本以为你能吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you thought you would?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太合适了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到不久前  电影拍摄还主要在摄影棚内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until recently, filmmaking was largely confined to the studios,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在这一过程有所发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but now the process has opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿贝尔·冈斯去年的《拿破仑》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abel Gance's Napoléon last year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现了摄影机在外景地的前景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}showed what a camera can do on location,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在真实的房子  场地拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}filming in real houses, real landscapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是部什么样的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What sort of film is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《赌徒》背景设在1875年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Gambler is set in 1875.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位伯爵的女儿  安·厄斯金小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An earl's daughter, Lady Anne Erskine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱上了一个男人  结果此人是个赌徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}falls in love with a man who turns out to be a gambler,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让她的家人十分惊恐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to her family's horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不难想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在乡下的一场别墅宴会上结识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They meet at a house party in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快情况就一发不可收拾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and things soon spin out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还去了一间很时髦的赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are visits to a smart gambling club,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在这里拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which we'd do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在唐顿开赌场吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A gambling club at Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这非要了奶奶的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would finish Granny off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Papa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们需要时间考虑  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We must have time to think. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的名片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任何问题就联系我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ring me if you have any questions at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会叫巴罗来送你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get Barrow to see you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有两个问题需要先问清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose there are two questions that we would need the answer to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能真正开始讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before we can really have the discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会待一个月左右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd be here for about a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把名片翻过来  我写了我们的出价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and if you turn the card over, you'll see what we'd pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  这还是可以商量的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, that's negotiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再见  巴伯先生  -再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Goodbye, Mr. Barber. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还只是起价吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's the starting point?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这主意糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's a horrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓妆艳抹的女演员和醉醺醺的男演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actresses plastered in makeup and actors just plastered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗手粗脚地动我们的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}scrambling over our things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得时刻注意餐具室丢没丢勺子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd have to keep counting the spoons in the pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本地人可能不会高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The locals might take a dim view.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别为此就放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you mustn't let that stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郡民们看什么都不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The county takes a dim view of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得考虑费用的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to consider the fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不需要谈钱的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't need to talk about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您得考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you need to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的不说  您可以重修屋顶了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could have a new roof, for a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不修要发大水了  那可如何是好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could soon be looking at real flooding, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you turn them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能不能说服他们北上去布兰克斯特堡呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you think we could persuade them to drive further north to Brancaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  您怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mama, where do you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽  亲爱的  你可以带你父亲去阁楼看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary, dear, will you take your father to see the attics?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他是好久没上去过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think he's been there for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都好些年没上来过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't been up here for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们面临的就是这样的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is the situation we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了钱  我们就能把房子修缮好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the money, we can bring the house up to snuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以匹配我们对庄园的投入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to match what we've spent on the estate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能抬头挺胸地迈入30年代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and enter the 1930s with our heads held high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但如果您不愿意...  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But if you don't want to... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你掌舵向前吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you steer ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在是船长了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我是知道的  哪怕你以为我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am aware of that, even if you think I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得我去把消息告诉卡森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now I have the unenviable task
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是什么美差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of breaking the news to Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里拍电影  他们能这么做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To make a film here? Can they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有电影明星来吗  著名影星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would there be film stars? Famous ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她点水吧  免得她晕过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, give her some water before she passes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情还没定下呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing's decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是可以激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all very fine to get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你住在农场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You live at the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其余的人时时刻刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest of us will have them in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要看着他们进进出出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and round about every hour God sends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且老夫人怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what of Her Ladyship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想要安度晚年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hoping for a peaceful end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却突然被丢进了一个杂牌马戏团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and suddenly plunged into a three-ring circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赞同黛西的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I agree with Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有机会认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get to know men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只在大银幕上见过的男女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've only seen upon the silver screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-如果这对房子有好处  -这就是重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And if it's good for the house... - This is the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有钱流入或许会至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An injection of cash could make all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们提到数了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They mention how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便提了也与我们无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not our business if they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们没说  -再见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They did not. - Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再见  -再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  休斯太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good night, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何  时代在变  我们也得跟上脚步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still, times change and we must change with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克太太  我们也该回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Parker. We should be getting home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  帕克先生  我这就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good, Mr. Parker. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西对他可比对我听话多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daisy's more obedient with him than she ever was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他让她更开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he makes her happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I did me best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A moving picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在唐顿拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it sounds unlikely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也没那么可怕吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm not sure it's quite as awful as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗鲁粗俗的演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rough and vulgar actors and actresses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在各个房间里走动  手脚还不干净\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}strolling through the rooms with their sticky fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在英国国王曾用餐的桌子旁的椅子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sitting on the chairs, eating at the table where the King of England once sat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直跟法国大革命最糟的情况有的一拼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, this smacks of the worst excesses of the French Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们要让他们不许坐下  戴上手套吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we ask them to stay standing and put them in gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是衰落  艾尔希\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a comedown, Elsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是下滑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a falling-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是跟暴民政治眉来眼去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are flirting with mob rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有钱拿  查理  他们又需要钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it will pay, Charlie, and they need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的话  干吗不对公众开放大宅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, by that argument, why not open the place to the public
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们把每个角落都看个遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and have them poke and pry in every corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这么做过一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We tried that once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后不是都决定再没有下次了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I thought we'd all decided never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再这么下去  要犯心脏病了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You carry on like that, you'll give yourself a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们沦落至此  那我还不如结束痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be better off out of it if this is what we've come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪  你能把报纸折好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Andy, I wonder if you might fold that newspaper properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拿去楼上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take it upstairs with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大宅要拍电影了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, moving picture to be made at the big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对你们会意味着什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will that mean for the pair of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不好说  -但肯定很让人激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can't say exactly. - But it'll be exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看电影怎么拍的  见到明星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seeing how a film's made, meeting the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你还是离他们远远的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd keep clear of them if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远离这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep clear of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就道晚安了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll say good night, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good night. - Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了一通还忘了拿报纸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgot the paper after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子真不好使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Memory like a sieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了  这是他的农场  不是我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember, it's his farm, not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是格兰瑟姆伯爵的农场  他只是佃户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Lord Grantham's farm, and he's only the tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别说什么你会后悔的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't say anything you'll regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早晚会说错话  那我们怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm bound to in the end, and then where will we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫里让人把遗嘱翻译好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Murray's had the will translated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说  蒙米拉提到他结婚前还年轻时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, Montmirail refers to an idyllic interlude
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟妈妈曾有过一段诗意的短暂情缘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he spent with Mama as a young man before he was married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫里还说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What else did Murray have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗孀想抵抗遗嘱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The widow wants to fight the will,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但儿子则认为可以友好地解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the son believes it can be settled in a friendly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我就拿铁丝网把别墅围起来  拿板子把窗户遮上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd cover the villa with barbed wire and board up the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他希望我们去一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He says he'd like us to visit him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈显然无法远行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, clearly Mama can't travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他叫我们带上汤姆和露西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he asked us to bring Tom and Lucy with us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他得知茜玻将成为继承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now that he knows Sybbie is to be the beneficiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有机会了解露西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we could get to know Lucy better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果走运的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with any luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能因此完全错过玛丽可怕的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would mean we'd miss the whole of Mary's frightful film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了  莫娜·达格利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found it. Myrna Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道我有张她的靓照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew I had a good one of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是美得经典\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her beauty is so classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有张他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got one of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖·德克斯特饰演《卡萨诺瓦》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guy Dexter in Casanova.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光是想想就脸红\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The very thought of it makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是不一般\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像一只要扑上来的野兽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like a wild animal ready to spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要扑倒你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready to spring on you, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不小心的话  安迪和我要吃醋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll have Andy and me jealous if you don't watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可敢情好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾你要错过乐趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate that you'll miss all the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都紧张了  让你单独接触盖·德克斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm nervous now, leaving you alone with Guy Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chance would be a fine thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你觉得呢  伯蒂  -有麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you think, Bertie? - A complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆说他们还得带上莫德·巴格肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom says they'd have to bring Maud Bagshaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的房子整理好之前她跟他们住在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's living with them until her house is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以一起住旅馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can all stay in an hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话  我们可以去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that case, can we come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会碍事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't be in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么除了我  大家都去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So everyone's going except me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在考虑写一篇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been thinking about an article
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于夏季去南法度假的人的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the people who visit the south of France in the summer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又写作了吗  太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you writing again? I'm pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊迪丝每周几天会回杂志社工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Edith's back at the magazine for a couple of days a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小彼得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And little Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的保姆很好  谢天谢地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has a wonderful nanny, thank heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着两个孩子  还要打理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you really work with two young children
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰克斯特堡  还能工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while running a house like Brancaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过六个月再问我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask me in six months' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴你又开始动脑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm glad to hear you're doing something with your brain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她的脑子还在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's hope it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天致电蒙米拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll telephone Montmirail tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他说我们会住酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and explain we'll be in an hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该会感到如释重负\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should think he'll be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到灯还亮着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the light was still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也赞成爸爸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose you agree with Papa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为电影的事太粗俗  不值得考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the whole idea of a film is too common to even be considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能帮助唐顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing is too common
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡过难关  那就没什么事"太粗俗"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if it will help to keep Downton afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就有钱重修屋顶了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'd have enough money for a new roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要忍受一个月的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the cost of one terrible month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  我的确觉得会是折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Honestly, I do think it will be pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但阁楼里用老洗脸盆接雨水的景象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the sight of old washbasins catching rainwater in the attics
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让人难受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is terrible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们撑过了战争  这也不在话下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got through the war. We can get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你一定要强硬  玛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you must be firm, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些人看来  我们这种女人只分两类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To those people, women like us fall into two categories:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霸王和蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}dragons and fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要让他们把你当霸王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must make sure they think of you as a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝茨先生和巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Bates and Miss Baxter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会去照顾格兰瑟姆伯爵和夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will go to look after Lord and Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人留在唐顿  帮助摄制组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest will stay at Downton to help with the film people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别指望我帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get no help from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟不肯帮忙小姐不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In contrast to Miss Won't-Lift-a-Finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd love to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做达格利什小姐的贴身女仆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could I be Miss Dalgleish's lady's maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经让安娜来做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've asked Anna to take that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想扫兴  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to be a spoilsport, Daisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你在这里还有工作要做呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you do have a job down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐的确要在宅子里住吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know Miss Dalgleish is staying in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  还有导演和男主演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is, with the director and the leading man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人会去村子里住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest are going to put up in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去见玛丽小姐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I need to go and see Lady Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, don't worry, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜会想办法让你见他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anna will find a way to get you in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是宁可去南法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd exchange it all for a trip to the south of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他很反对  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's opposed, I'm afraid, milady,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说他必须来守着  让他们不敢逾越\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and says he must stand watch and keep them in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道这是不是帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how helpful that will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得想办法让他走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该跟其他人一起去南法  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should travel to France with the rest of the party? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她担心老爷会觉得一切都奇怪  陌生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She worries that everything will be odd and foreign for His Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而贝茨先生和巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And neither Mr. Bates nor Miss Baxter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又都不能指挥人把一切都安排妥当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will have the authority to make sure it's all done properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷需要你  查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His Lordship needs you, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能让他们知道该怎么做事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only you can show them how things should be managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你就别担心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们最好给我小心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'd better be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国人要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The British are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我该拿他怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what would I do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这不是太麻烦蒙米拉一家了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And wouldn't it be rather an imposition on the Montmirails?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直都希望能帮上您  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He longs to be useful to you, Papa, as he always did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就不能让他觉得  光是他的存在就帮到了您吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couldn't you give him the feeling that he'd help you just by being there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坚持的话也行  但这也太感情用事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will if you insist, but it seems very sentimental to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你们  停在他后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, you lot, go behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two, come on, pull along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跟服装管理员走  -把那个递给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Follow the wardrobe mistress. - Pass me those.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她会给你们指路  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She'll show you where to go. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  那是私人房间  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, that's private. - Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这边  -在这里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This way. - Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, please. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  莫斯利先生  你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Mr. Molesley. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我喜欢关于电影的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I love anything to do with films.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你喜欢去看电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know you enjoy a trip to the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, it's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好莱坞就是终极梦工厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me, Hollywood is the ultimate dream factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像所有人一样需要梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I need dreams as much as the next man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女人这么多行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this for one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是达格利什小姐的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I give you Miss Dalgleish's wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但多高档啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, but just fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  好好弄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稳稳当当的  各位  往前走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice and steady, lads. Keep it moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-非常感谢  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you very much. - Right you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心脚下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch your footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都在这儿  躲着入侵者呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you're all here, hiding from the invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜玻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sybbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a lovely surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆把她送了过来  这样我们去南法时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom had her driven so she could be with her cousins
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可以跟表弟妹们一起玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while we're in France.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在谈你的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, we've been talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗  阿驴  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About me, Donk? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多原因  都是好原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any number of reasons, all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我介绍  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I present Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲  格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father, Lord Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是电影的一位影星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is one of the stars of our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can easily believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到唐顿  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Downton, Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现代世界来到了唐顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The modern world comes to Downton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您跟法国的东道主说了我们会住酒店了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've told our host in France that we're staying at an hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不肯接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, he wouldn't hear of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他坚持我们要去别墅住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He insists we stay at the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕我们是去从他们手中偷走别墅的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even though we're there to steal it from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎是个很不错的家伙  英语也说得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He seems a very nice chap, and his English is flawless,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.06,0:23:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的法语可没那么好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is more than can be said for my French.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖·德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Guy Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome, Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Lord Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我女儿  玛丽·塔伯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my daughter, Lady Mary Talbot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会照顾你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll look after you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其他人要去里维埃拉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the rest of us are off to the Riviera.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你在这里会待得愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I hope you'll enjoy yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的话我真想跟你们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd come with you if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是英国人啊  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're English? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十年前去了美国碰运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went over to America ten years ago to try my luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后便一直待在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I've been there ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止我一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被称为好莱坞英裔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They call us the Hollywood Raj,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每周会打一次板球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we all play cricket once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会因为天气停赛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the weather never stops play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过南法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上次去时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last time I was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟罗纳德·科曼和格洛丽娅·斯旺森一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was marooned on the roof of the Negresco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被困在了内格莱斯科酒店的屋顶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with Ronald Colman and Gloria Swanson.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋顶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭时告诉我们故事的后半段吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can tell us the rest of that story at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们什么时候出发  -明天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When are you leaving? - Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从多佛去加莱  然后乘蓝色列车去尼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, Dover, Calais and then the Blue Train down to Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:23:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去让人羡慕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How enviable that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们导演什么时候来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When do you expect your director?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他晚饭时会来的  是吧  莫娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, he'll be here for dinner. Don't you think, Myrna?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫娜·达格利什就在这房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myrna Dalgleish in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.75,0:24:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她爸就在老博罗市场卖水果  看她现在多发达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her dad sold fruit in the old Borough Market. Now look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了银幕女神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A goddess of the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.38,0:24:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能做她的女仆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're going to be her maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.34,0:24:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她带来了一堆行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's brought a mountain of luggage,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和安娜不如现在过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I thought you and Anna could go together right now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮她收拾一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and offer to unpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.18,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住  你们都不了解这女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just remember, neither of you know this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.43,0:24:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她或许并不是你们在影迷杂志上读到的那位电影明星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She may not be the film star you see in the fan magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看便知了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.65,0:24:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰瑟姆伯爵夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉突然造访\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to burst in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.70,0:24:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.58,0:24:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  我立了新遗嘱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fact is I've made a new will,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你们见证我签名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I need you both to witness my signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是没事找事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.25,0:24:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就是我的珠宝和其他一些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only my jewelry and a few other pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.58,0:24:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及时更新遗嘱一向是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always a good idea to bring these things up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.09,0:25:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好莫里也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Murray was down anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.21,0:25:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想借此机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I thought I would take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好你来了  因为我想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you've come, because I wanted to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.51,0:25:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维奥莱特叫我们整理她的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Violet has asked us to go through her things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.51,0:25:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  她为什么找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Why has she asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.01,0:25:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的不知道  不过真要有什么重要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really don't know, but, of course, anything of interest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.77,0:25:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会告诉你和罗伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will be referred to Robert and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.60,0:25:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得该告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just thought you ought to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想把后事都安排好  不用再为此烦恼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she wants her death to be ordered and free of bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.31,0:25:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是维奥莱特的作风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all very Violet-like, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们是不是不该去法国  -当然不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are we wrong to go to France? - Oh, certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.28,0:25:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真有什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary can send a telegram
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.65,0:25:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽可以发电报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if there are any dark developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会假装我一向把她奉若神明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't pretend I've always worshipped at her shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没了她肯定会很别扭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it will be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等她走了  玛丽肯定会想她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Mary will miss her when she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.08,0:25:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽会成为她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary will become her,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就后继有人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the gap will be filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.25,0:25:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶紧走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now I must run.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.25,0:25:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这趟耽误晚餐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm making dinner late by being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.47,0:25:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们回来再见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.97,0:25:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说得对  会很别扭的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's right. It will be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.26,0:25:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会怀念有个斗嘴的伴儿让我保持状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall miss having a sparring partner to keep me trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.44,0:26:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿那些衣服可小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful how you handle them clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.44,0:26:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是高定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're haute couture.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去给玛丽小姐和赫克瑟姆夫人更衣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should go to Lady Mary and Lady Hexham to help them dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.36,0:26:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就让黛西帮您收拾行李了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I'll leave Daisy with the unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.61,0:26:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等您去吃饭了我再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be back when you're at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.45,0:26:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我上来时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So long as it's finished
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.53,0:26:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都收拾好了  行李箱也都收起来了就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the trunks are gone when I come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.45,0:26:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么会在内格莱斯科酒店的屋顶上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you doing on the roof of the Negresco?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.91,0:26:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在玩寻宝  需要一个烟囱顶帽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it was a scavenger hunt, and we needed a chimney pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.62,0:26:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们上去才发现  那玩意好大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when we got up there, they were huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.54,0:26:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就砸了一个  各拿了一块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so we smashed one and all took a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经理怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, was the manager pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.26,0:26:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有利于宣传\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it was good publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.84,0:26:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有有利宣传这种事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there such a thing as good publicity?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.64,0:26:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于拍电影来说有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is if you're in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.10,0:26:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄国人会砸玻璃祈福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I suppose the Russians smash their glasses for good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.18,0:26:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演艺人士会砸别人的财产好获得有利宣传\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now film people smash other people's property for good publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.98,0:26:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this true, Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.69,0:26:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只做我想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I don't do nothing unless I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.82,0:26:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得真好听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, how musical you make it sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:26:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把盘子端近点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold the plate nearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.41,0:26:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么当上电影演员的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you become a film actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.70,0:26:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个星探发现了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A talent scout spotted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:26:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.12,0:27:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太浪漫了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems wonderfully romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没那么浪漫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not that romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.25,0:27:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟房间里每个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not when you know that every man in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.67,0:27:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都只想跟你来一发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just wants to give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.88,0:27:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生活真是精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a colorful life you lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.05,0:27:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在国内拍过很多电影吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}H-Have you made many kinematographs traveling around the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.64,0:27:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴我会错过这个过程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I'm rather glad to be missing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.60,0:27:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你只是因为钱才同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know you're only doing it for the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.18,0:27:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.56,0:27:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法理解你们怎么能记住那么多台词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I never understand is how you remember all those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是舞台剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.98,0:27:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  我都不确定这算是演戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I'm not even sure it's proper acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.03,0:27:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但情况不是要变了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, but isn't that about to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.86,0:27:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影不是要有声了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't films starting to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.82,0:27:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是一两句吧  不会惊到马的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couple of words here or there. Nothing to frighten the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.41,0:27:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.99,0:27:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我杯薄荷甜酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me a crème de menthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.91,0:27:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能提醒达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would it be possible to remind Miss Dalgleish
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.42,0:27:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家里的仆人都很辛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the servants work hard in this house
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.50,0:27:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也都尽全力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they are doing their best?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.00,0:27:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不习惯粗鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not used to rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.46,0:27:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还不习惯被批评呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she's not used to criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的脸在银幕上能卖上百万张票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her face on the screen sells a million tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这她清楚得很  -干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and she knows it. - Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.01,0:27:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.69,0:28:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我20岁时拍了第一部电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I got my first picture when I was 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.77,0:28:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.44,0:28:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是管家  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the butler, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.49,0:28:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您需要什么尽管跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please tell me if there's anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.86,0:28:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything I need?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不好办到吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems rather a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我逗你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm-I'm teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说  我什么都不缺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I should've said was I have everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.13,0:28:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.04,0:28:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那本旅行指南放下  睡觉吧  查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, put that guidebook down, Charlie, and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.01,0:28:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看完这章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm, let me finish the chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.44,0:28:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会相信这些人都吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't believe what these people eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.36,0:28:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-走吧  卡森  -借过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, Carson. - Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.49,0:29:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们逃吧  赶在情况恶化之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's run for it before things get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.04,0:29:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你为地中海气候准备了一套衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you've got a Mediterranean version of that outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.75,0:29:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你会热死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you'll boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.09,0:29:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心我  老爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about me, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.42,0:29:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要乖乖的  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're going to be good, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.26,0:29:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.55,0:29:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-照顾好提奥  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look after Teo. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.39,0:29:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要玩得愉快  不管他们什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, have a lovely time, no matter what they're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.47,0:29:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我们尽力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.35,0:29:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟人起冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, don't get into any scrapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.19,0:29:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现  跟外国人相处时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have found, when dealing with foreigners,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.56,0:29:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大声慢速说话  他们就会听从你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if one speaks loudly and slowly, they'll bend to your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也别太大声  别太慢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not too loudly and not too slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.94,0:29:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  安德鲁  不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, no, no, Andrew. Andrew. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.45,0:29:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  贝茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Bates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来祝你们好运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've come to wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.62,0:29:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们赶得正好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you only just caught us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.70,0:29:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要踏上奇怪的征途了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as we set off on our strange mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.63,0:29:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.59,0:29:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾你要错过拍摄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry you'll miss the filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.46,0:29:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不在时  你要来看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you watch it while we're away?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.13,0:29:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们让我就来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will if they let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.55,0:29:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try and enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.14,0:30:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用嘱咐你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No need to say the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定让约翰尼别惹祸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please make sure that Johnnie keeps his nose clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.22,0:30:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.98,0:30:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都上车  不然我们要误车了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone aboard or we'll miss the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过这么多美丽的女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't think I've ever seen so many lovely-looking ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.54,0:30:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐要喝茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cup of tea for Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.12,0:30:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚泡了茶  让黛西端过去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've just made some. Daisy can take it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.08,0:30:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吧  我想去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'll do that. I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  让我去吧  求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, let me. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.17,0:30:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽小姐不会介意的  我求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Mary won't mind. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.96,0:30:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别着急  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Steady on, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.26,0:30:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我去把盘子端回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, but I'll fetch the tray after.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.44,0:30:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给您的  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is for you, Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.65,0:31:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直没机会告诉您  您的到来多让人兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never got chance to say how exciting it is that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.41,0:31:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好喜欢您的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love your pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.20,0:31:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您给了我很大的激励\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been such an inspiration to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.49,0:31:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我第一次看《不幸的…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since I first saw Star-Crossed...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.70,0:31:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以赶紧开始吗  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can we get a move on? - Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.33,0:31:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Positions, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.83,0:31:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是那个女演员吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's the actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.71,0:31:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roll the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.21,0:31:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.51,0:31:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And action!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走下楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You walk downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.72,0:31:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and find him with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.05,0:31:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你停住脚步  然后继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You halt and walk on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.02,0:31:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他在等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.02,0:31:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她说她很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her she looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.02,0:31:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话让你很高兴  但又不能承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're delighted to hear it, but you cannot admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.69,0:31:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看着他的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.24,0:31:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会允许他吻你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you let him kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.41,0:31:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels as if you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.91,0:31:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait! Wait! Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.78,0:31:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut, cut, cut, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.45,0:31:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So-- I'm ever so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  这样我没法工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, I-I can't work like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.04,0:31:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是莫斯利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's Molesley.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.79,0:31:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a great favorite here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.25,0:31:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不介意他看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't mind him watching, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.13,0:31:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定不介意他看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure they don't mind him watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.13,0:31:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只是不希望他入镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just don't want him in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.46,0:32:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Well spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.13,0:32:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要再拍一次吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So now you just do it all again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.43,0:32:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁可去井下挖煤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd rather earn my living down a mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.80,0:32:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回归原位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First positions please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.01,0:32:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roll the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.18,0:32:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.23,0:32:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And action!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.39,0:32:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他又来了一次  -走下楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As if he did that again. - Coming down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.44,0:32:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他就在那里等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not expecting to find him there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我知道我们都会住在别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'd known we were all going to be staying at the villa,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.57,0:32:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我可能就不会来了  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not sure I'd have come. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.95,0:32:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得会尴尬吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't think it might be a little awkward?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.37,0:32:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们偷走了这家人的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we've appropriated this family's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.50,0:32:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想不对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure that's the sensible way to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴茜玻跟她的表亲会更平等些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just glad Sybbie will be on much more equal terms with her cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.80,0:32:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维奥莱特给了你的孩子一个大好机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Violet is giving your child a great opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.01,0:32:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个好起点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a real start in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的慷慨不让你意外吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does her generosity surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.10,0:32:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匈奴王阿提拉也爱他的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attila the Hun loved his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.15,0:32:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧  卡森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right, Mr. Carson?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.40,0:33:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"All right" Is not the first phrase that springs to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.28,0:33:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给您拿了点鸡汤来  卡森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've brought you some chicken soup, Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.47,0:33:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她听上去很粗鲁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she sounds very rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.68,0:33:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她大概是累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect she's done in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.14,0:33:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整部电影都指望着你  肯定很辛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it must be difficult when the whole film depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.85,0:33:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德克斯特先生不也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It depends on Mr. Dexter, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.10,0:33:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可他就很有礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he seems very well-mannered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还那么帅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.15,0:33:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么心思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.11,0:33:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便我有  我会告诉你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I were, would I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.90,0:33:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯利先生也被拍进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Molesley's in the film now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.90,0:33:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道该站哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wasn't sure where to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.28,0:33:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是让拍电影的去拍电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't we let the film people get on with their work
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.57,0:33:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做好自己的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while we get on with ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听他的  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to him, Daisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.20,0:33:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急着跑去加入马戏团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before you run away to join the circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.43,0:34:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都还好吧  都没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say, how are we all? How did we all survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.55,0:34:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还好吗  -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.98,0:35:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们走吧  -海真蓝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, shall we? - Oh, the color of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙米拉先生吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur de Montmirail?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.74,0:35:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰瑟姆伯爵  欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord Grantham. Bienvenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.28,0:35:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来的人挺多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we've become quite a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们连管家都带来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid we've even brought our butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.74,0:35:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not quite sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.12,0:35:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真时髦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how chic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.45,0:35:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, come in, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.04,0:35:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来吧  -我得喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - Just going to feel like I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.50,0:35:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想坐会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I could do with a sit-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.87,0:35:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.34,0:35:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.22,0:35:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.60,0:35:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我介绍格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I present Lord Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.85,0:35:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲  蒙米拉侯爵夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mother. La Marquise de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.73,0:35:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.52,0:35:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是格兰瑟姆夫人  赫克瑟姆侯爵和夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, this is Lady Grantham, Lord and Lady Hexham,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.11,0:35:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴格肖夫人和布兰森先生先生和太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Bagshaw and Mr. And Mrs. Branson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.32,0:35:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布兰森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, Monsieur Branson,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.03,0:35:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位幸运孩子的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}father of the lucky child.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.69,0:35:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定很高兴吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How happy you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.78,0:35:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我妻子很高兴能来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My wife and I are very glad to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.49,0:35:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得说  很感谢您愿意招待我们这一群人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must say straightaway how kind you are to include us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.49,0:35:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很荣幸  赫克瑟姆侯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're delighted, Lord Hexham.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.08,0:36:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't we, maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.71,0:36:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  帕特莫太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mrs. Patmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.63,0:36:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -慢点吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Uh, mind you eat them slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.21,0:36:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.84,0:36:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗  你要回农场去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you? Are you on your way back to the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.14,0:36:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让那小两口歇歇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to give the young couple a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.22,0:36:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都没有独处时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.26,0:36:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总得忍受我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They always have to put up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.72,0:36:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你家  你想怎样就怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's your house to do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.02,0:36:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望他们觉得那是他们的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I want them to feel it's their home,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.35,0:36:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样等我不再租了  他们就会接手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that when I surrender the tenancy, they'll take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.31,0:36:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.61,0:36:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别担心我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.98,0:36:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要操心自己的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've got your own concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.78,0:36:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I do worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.11,0:36:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.74,0:36:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的拍摄日程表一小时后发下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call sheets for tomorrow will be issued in an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.08,0:36:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送到你们的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and delivered to your digs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.95,0:36:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还顺利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A good day?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能按进度进行就算顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always good if we get through the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  好消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that? Good news, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.00,0:36:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.71,0:36:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫要比预期的迟些回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My husband isn't coming back when he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.21,0:36:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定很失望吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must be a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.92,0:36:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失望  但不意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a disappointment but not a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.17,0:36:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八点半太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half past 8:00 is too late for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要七点吃饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like to eat at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.22,0:36:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变常规时间安排很难为厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's difficult for the kitchen if we change the usual timings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真看不出她有什么明星魔力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I could see the star magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.44,0:37:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.69,0:37:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟斯克在放映她的一部电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of her films is showing in Thirsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.11,0:37:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起去看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't we catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.40,0:37:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.73,0:37:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家人都不在  你可以自己做主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None of your family's here. You're your own mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.36,0:37:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.86,0:37:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去告诉巴罗  换件大衣  然后告诉奶奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll warn Barrow, put on a coat and tell Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.00,0:37:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶  别生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Granny, don't be cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.67,0:37:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要去瑟斯克看电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm going into Thirsk to see a film.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.38,0:37:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟导演巴伯先生去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Mr. Barber, the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.71,0:37:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利最近来信儿了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard from Henry lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.80,0:37:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今天发来封电报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He sent a telegram today.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.26,0:37:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他暂时还不回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not coming back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.72,0:37:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹可  计划有变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Denker, change of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不更衣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.97,0:37:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿托盘吃晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have my dinner on a tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.52,0:37:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.32,0:37:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.24,0:38:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐像疣一样讨厌又不怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not your fault that Miss Dalgleish has all the charm of a verruca.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.07,0:38:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德克斯特先生还挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Mr. Dexter's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.70,0:38:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可以自己应付她  不需要我帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can stick up for himself without my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.58,0:38:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您对拍电影不感兴趣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't filming interest you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I watched some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.25,0:38:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁可去吃石头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd rather eat pebbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.88,0:38:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是上床吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I think I'll retire to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.96,0:38:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少待到他们走了为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least until they've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.38,0:38:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要担心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.55,0:38:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛伦斯·南丁格尔38岁就上床了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Florence Nightingale took to her bed at the age of 38.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.72,0:38:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她90岁才死呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She died at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.47,0:38:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您会告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would tell me, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.81,0:38:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.02,0:38:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.65,0:38:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢  格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you, Lord Grantham?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.90,0:38:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你熟悉南法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you familiar with the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.99,0:38:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道1830年代布鲁厄姆男爵做大法官时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know Lord Brougham first made it fashionable
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.20,0:38:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先让来南法成为了潮流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the 1830s when he was chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.29,0:38:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你只是在拿回本就属于你的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're only taking back what is yours by right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.46,0:38:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.58,0:38:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我理解这为什么让你不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I do see why you find it upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.17,0:38:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你还是来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But here you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.71,0:38:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打量家具  丈量窗帘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}eyeing up the furniture, measuring the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.63,0:38:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:38:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还可以买别的别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can always buy another villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来是应你儿子的邀请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're here because your son invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想我也是想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I suppose I would like to know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.85,0:39:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丈夫为什么这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why your husband did what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.81,0:39:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经叫律师过几天来一趟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've asked our lawyer to join us here in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样甚好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.02,0:39:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前  希望你们都住得愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until then, I hope you'll enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.19,0:39:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的管家让我们的日常更加气派了  这可真棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your butler lends a welcome air of splendor to the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想  可以让他退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he can stand down if you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.49,0:39:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必呢  别墅已经是你外孙女的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, when the villa already belongs to your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.78,0:39:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴格肖夫人  快来坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Bagshaw, please come and sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.96,0:39:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.62,0:39:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就闭眼躺了五分钟  就睡过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I laid down for five minutes, shut my eyes, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.92,0:39:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得沉沉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.54,0:39:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到鸽子别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to the Villa of the Doves.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.17,0:39:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们经常来吧  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You must come here a lot. - We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前是的  在你们出现之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or rather, we did, before you entered our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.80,0:39:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我有记忆以来  每年冬天都来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always in the winter for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.47,0:39:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在  夏季来玩也时髦了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now coming in the warmer months is catching on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.22,0:39:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算就此写篇文章呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm planning an article on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.02,0:39:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是作家吗  赫克瑟姆夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a writer, Lady Hexham?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.39,0:39:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是记者还差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More of a journalist, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.31,0:39:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有本杂志  我打算重新掌控它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a magazine, and I'm taking back control of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.27,0:39:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的文章是写什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your article about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.65,0:40:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯考特·菲茨杰拉德  塞尔达  可可·香奈儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, uh, Scott Fitzgerald, Zelda, Coco Chanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.86,0:40:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有让酒店七月继续迎客的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the people that got the hotels to stay open in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.53,0:40:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以发布一些别墅的照片吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I publish some pictures of the villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.16,0:40:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might that be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.87,0:40:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.08,0:40:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发布前要让我们看看照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we can see the images before you use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.17,0:40:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他显然不是第一次跟记者打交道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, you're obviously not the first journalist he's met.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.21,0:40:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请出示影票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tickets, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能改日再欣赏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to have to defer our appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.59,0:40:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐的魅力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Miss Dalgleish's attractions to another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.35,0:40:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是她的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't her film.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.47,0:40:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《惊恐》是英国上映的第一部有声片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Terror is the first all-talking picture to show in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.14,0:40:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是《爵士歌手》吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought that was The Jazz Singer. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.10,0:40:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那部里  阿尔·乔生只是对他的老母亲说了几句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that, Al Jolson just says a few words to his old mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.69,0:40:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, and sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.52,0:40:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部电影可以是从头说到尾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this, they talk all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.03,0:40:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽都影院在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the Rialto?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.28,0:40:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面左转停车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, take the next left and park.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.33,0:40:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽小姐跟巴伯先生去瑟斯克看电影了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Mary's gone to the pictures in Thirsk with Mr. Barber,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰瑟姆老夫人要在房间里吃饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and old Lady Grantham's eating in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.42,0:41:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德克斯特先生和达格利什小姐会单独进餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So Mr. Dexter and Miss Dalgleish will be dining alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.84,0:41:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您告诉帕特莫太太了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you let Mrs. Patmore know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.42,0:41:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都可怜德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all pity Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.09,0:41:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.55,0:41:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不会想知道的  休斯太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you wouldn't be interested, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.47,0:41:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来听听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.39,0:41:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.24,0:41:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王室来访时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we had the royal visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.86,0:41:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您记得有个叫埃利斯的贴身男仆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do you remember a valet called Ellis?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.87,0:41:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你和他还挺亲近的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and he were quite friendly, I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.96,0:41:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今早收到了一封他的来信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a letter from him this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.21,0:41:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他要结婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}saying he's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.55,0:41:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让你难过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.34,0:41:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我不该这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.05,0:41:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴罗先生  你的人生路很艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Barrow, your path in life is a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.52,0:41:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分与你处境相同的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most people in your position
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:41:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会选择藏在假象之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}choose to hide behind appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.31,0:42:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此避免遭到迫害和拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that will allow them to avoid persecution and rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.57,0:42:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不该因此被责怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's surely not to be blamed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.03,0:42:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想如此  休斯太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It isn't what I want, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.99,0:42:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是个勇敢的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you're a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.28,0:42:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也注定要孤独了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're also destined to be a lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.50,0:42:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你非常幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you're very fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.31,0:42:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说她的脸能卖上百万张票吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you said her face could sell a million tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.19,0:42:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来在瑟斯克不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not in Thirsk, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.78,0:42:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.57,0:42:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.84,0:43:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How wonderful this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.76,0:43:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不懂为什么让我们过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still curious as to why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.05,0:43:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你去英国  就能见到我妈妈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'd come to England, you could have met Mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.26,0:43:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样更合理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which would've made more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.97,0:43:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想见你  而不是格兰瑟姆老夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was you I wanted to meet more than old Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.85,0:43:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你母亲呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的处境要更微妙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The situation is more delicate for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.61,0:43:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.69,0:43:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.20,0:43:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.16,0:43:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们打的什么主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do think their game is?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.49,0:43:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们放松警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To lull us into a sense of security
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.20,0:43:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再突然提起诉讼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then whack us with a lawsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.66,0:43:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他们是想让我们感到愧疚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe they want us to feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.25,0:43:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and withdraw from the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.41,0:43:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得蒙米拉先生只是爱他的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's just that Monsieur de Montmirail loved his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.29,0:43:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想执行他的遗愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he intends to carry out his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.29,0:43:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们则代表奶奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're here to represent Granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.25,0:43:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事里的神秘人物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the mystery figure in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.20,0:44:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bonjour, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺眼  不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glare. Um, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮蔽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.04,0:44:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}C-- Uh, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.33,0:44:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.41,0:44:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carson?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.29,0:44:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I be of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.80,0:44:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这顶就行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought maybe this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.34,0:44:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去像阿尔巴尼亚的佐格国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It makes you look like King Zog of Albania.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.97,0:44:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.31,0:44:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.06,0:44:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.23,0:44:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't hear of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.81,0:44:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我选的  我来付钱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my choice, so I should pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.40,0:44:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但戴帽子的是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but I'm the one who has to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.82,0:44:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的光顾  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for your custom, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.36,0:44:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您和您妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both you and your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.36,0:44:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\fs18\b1}两位演员是真夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.58,0:45:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你刚到好莱坞时在卖男装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were selling menswear when you first got to Hollywood,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.00,0:45:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么进入电影行业的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how did you break into films?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.91,0:45:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天  他们要求我穿一套他们在销售的西装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, one day, they asked me to pose for a trade journal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.46,0:45:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为一本行业杂志拍照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in a suit that they were marketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.04,0:45:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就来了个经纪人  跟我签了约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and an agent came and signed me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.13,0:45:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你太帅了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.51,0:45:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为他们是看上了我的演技呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought they were excited by my acting talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.72,0:45:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘们  快去换衣服吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, girls. Get to wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.26,0:45:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都想回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.76,0:45:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你知道我是怎么拍起电影的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you know why I'm in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.06,0:45:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么当上管家的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you become a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.85,0:45:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没那么风光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's a lot less glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.06,0:45:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我起初是门童\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a job as a hallboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.60,0:45:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是初级男仆  第一男仆  贴身男仆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I was a junior footman, first footman, valet
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.52,0:45:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终当上了管家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and finally butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.32,0:45:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起打理宅子  我可是无所不晓  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's not much I couldn't tell you about how to run a house, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.94,0:45:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你和我的区别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, that's the difference between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.03,0:45:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我半数时候都不知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what I'm doing half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.16,0:45:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去可不像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.24,0:45:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  你是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, thank you, Mr....?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.20,0:45:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴罗就行  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just Barrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.83,0:45:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  盖  我们彩排一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, Guy. Let's rehearse please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.42,0:45:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫娜  说台词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myrna, say the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.76,0:45:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你留了根木槌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saved you a mallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.80,0:46:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得它们看上去像是打仗用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always think they look like instruments of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.18,0:46:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为本来就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's because they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.43,0:46:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有电话找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a telephone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.97,0:46:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布洛克先生  说是急事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Mr. Bullock. He says it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.64,0:46:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家休息五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Five minutes, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.90,0:46:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楼下闹起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a drama going on below.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.52,0:46:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上楼时  那个负责人在冲着电话大喊大叫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man in charge was shouting down the telephone when I came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.65,0:46:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他们拍的电影不对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, they're making the wrong sort of film.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.15,0:46:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有对的电影吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a right sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.86,0:46:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道  公众似乎只想看有声电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, all I know is it seems the public only want films that talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.45,0:46:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为电影最棒的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've thought the best thing about films
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.50,0:46:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是听不到呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that you can't hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.96,0:46:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是看不见就更好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be even better if you couldn't see them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.96,0:46:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody, gather around, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.63,0:46:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.34,0:46:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要暂停拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are suspending production.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.88,0:46:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.18,0:46:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉带来坏消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to be the bearer of bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.51,0:46:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划定好后  便会联络大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll contact you all when we've finalized our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.47,0:46:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.48,0:46:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.85,0:46:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有声片的热度已经不容忽视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it seems the talkies are making too much money to ignore,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.82,0:46:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们拍的是默片  难以回本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}while our picture is silent and too expensive to make its costs back,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.07,0:46:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们想及时止损  中止拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they want to cut their losses and shut us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.86,0:47:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-太糟了  -对于剧组的人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But how sad. - It is worse than sad
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.99,0:47:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the men and women working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.74,0:47:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还欠群演工资呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We still owe our extras back pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.37,0:47:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下他们还失业了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now they're out of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.87,0:47:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我说了  -失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I told you. I... - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.62,0:47:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myrna.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.58,0:47:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么停了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}W-Why is he stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.13,0:47:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说默片现在不挣钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apparently, silent films aren't making any money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.92,0:47:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那晚看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw it the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.21,0:47:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影院里几乎是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The cinema was almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.72,0:47:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.84,0:47:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我替巴伯先生难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel sorry for Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.47,0:47:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他真不该这么惨  -够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He doesn't deserve this. - Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.35,0:47:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真希望能帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.35,0:47:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望你能帮忙  但你恐怕帮不上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you could, too, but I don't see how.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.15,0:47:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在拍默片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're making a silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.19,0:47:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他们只想发行有声片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They only want to release talkies, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.44,0:47:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能把这部电影改成有声片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, why couldn't this be turned into a talking film?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.32,0:47:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那需要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.03,0:47:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从伦敦叫一位技术员来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Getting a technician down from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.86,0:47:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可以给我们已经拍的戏录音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could record sound for scenes we've already made and...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.95,0:47:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给剩下的戏写新台词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then put new speeches into the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.83,0:47:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道不行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why wouldn't that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.96,0:47:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅森先生要把我逼疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Mason's driving me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.46,0:47:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个杯子碟子都要摆对地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every cup and saucer has to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.84,0:48:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实就是  你是他儿媳妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fact is you're his daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.05,0:48:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他儿子因战争而死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His son died in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.97,0:48:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪他和我相处不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it's no wonder he and I rub each other up the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.51,0:48:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜他这么惹你烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's a shame he's getting on your nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.47,0:48:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he's a lovely chap.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.31,0:48:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对你更是珍视  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he thinks the world of you, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.93,0:48:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前不还喜欢过他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weren't you sweet on him once?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.85,0:48:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都多少年前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About a hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.31,0:48:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说有位声音专家要从伦敦过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear there's a sound expert coming down from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.82,0:48:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提醒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.40,0:48:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.40,0:48:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.45,0:48:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没人能帮我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one can help me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.50,0:48:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.67,0:48:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是巴罗就行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it isn't Just Barrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.42,0:48:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.21,0:48:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是在想  这栋大宅子可比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've just been thinking how much more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.63,0:48:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们傻乎乎的电影有趣多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this great house is than our silly little film.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.97,0:48:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别喊我"先生"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't call me "Sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.09,0:48:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做点什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.72,0:48:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你能想到我接下来该去干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not unless you've got some ideas for my next career.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.35,0:48:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.02,0:48:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影之前一直是哑剧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Films have been mime until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.65,0:48:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哑剧加音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mime with music.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.44,0:49:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的有声片要看演技了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now with the new talkies, they're gonna be about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.11,0:49:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会想要我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't want us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.24,0:49:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会雇舞台剧的真演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll hire real actors from the theater, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.57,0:49:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.08,0:49:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的声音很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you've got a good voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.12,0:49:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会有新面孔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There may be new faces coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.75,0:49:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但公众也不会忘了所有他们最喜欢的老面孔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the public won't want to say goodbye to all their old favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.71,0:49:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.25,0:49:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.73,0:49:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是公爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the Duke...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.39,0:49:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威斯敏斯特公爵的游艇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the Duke of Westminster's yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.80,0:50:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me sum up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.59,0:50:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自1864年以来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the years since 1864,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.72,0:50:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过世的蒙米拉侯爵立过四份遗嘱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the late Marquis de Montmirail made four wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.60,0:50:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在每一封里都提到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In every one, he refers to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.81,0:50:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他1865年就将鸽子别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he gave the Villa des Colombes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.23,0:50:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给了如今的格兰瑟姆老伯爵夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the now Dowager Countess of Grantham in 1865.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.11,0:50:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带来了原件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I brought the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.57,0:50:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复件我留给你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will leave copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.11,0:50:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他显然不是忘了这回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then clearly it wasn't something that slipped his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.65,0:50:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的确想这么做  而且一直没改主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He meant to do this thing, and he stuck by his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.99,0:50:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我好受些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel better for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.20,0:50:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定抓住了他什么把柄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must have had some hold over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.12,0:50:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定是勒索了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She must have blackmailed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.66,0:50:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  这么想太傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman, this is a foolish response.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.70,0:50:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会告上法庭的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shall challenge it in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.75,0:50:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么理由呢  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On what basis, madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.92,0:50:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还有其他房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have other houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.29,0:50:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,困苦不是理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no question of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.09,0:50:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您丈夫买下别墅并做处理时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your husband bought the villa and disposed of it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.38,0:50:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不认识您呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before he even met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.38,0:50:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议您尽快把别墅交出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My advice would be to surrender the property without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.56,0:50:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.06,0:50:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你打算接受吗  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you mean to accept this? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.98,0:51:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲指名我为唯一的遗嘱执行人  格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father made me sole executor, Lord Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.11,0:51:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是因为他相信我会执行他的遗愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like to think it was because he trusted me to carry out his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.57,0:51:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么邀请我们来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why did you invite us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.20,0:51:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I was curious to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.91,0:51:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲和你母亲在1864年10月共度了一周\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father and your mother spent a week together in October 1864.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.46,0:51:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是1865年7月出生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I was born in July 1865.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.58,0:51:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.00,0:51:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他正是因此才在一个月后就把别墅送给了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think that's the key to why he gave her the villa one month later.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.55,0:51:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了庆祝你的出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In gratitude for your birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.47,0:51:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  我相信我们有很多共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In short, I believe you and I have a great deal in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.61,0:51:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们应该感谢老夫人  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We should thank old Lady Grantham. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.16,0:51:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我们现在知道  她得到别墅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least now we know that for her to have the villa
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.37,0:51:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非是因一时兴起或愚蠢失误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wasn't a random choice or a foolish mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.20,0:52:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是一个多年来未变的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but a decision that was firmly endorsed over many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.04,0:52:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉怪怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feels funny, in a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.79,0:52:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子属于这样一个黄金圈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to know my own child is part of this golden circle
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.00,0:52:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只因为血统就能遇上好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where, because of your blood, lovely things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.38,0:52:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像玛丽会得到唐顿  我们会得到布朗普顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as Mary will have Downton and we will have Brompton.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.47,0:52:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  但那都是运营庄园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but they're working estates.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.18,0:52:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方就是玩乐用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This place was made for laughter and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.80,0:52:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜玻难道不会为自己的女儿感到开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't Sybil have been pleased for her daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.93,0:52:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并鼓励她用它来帮助他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And encouraged her to use it for the good of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.81,0:52:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  她会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I think she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.19,0:52:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也这么做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then let's do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.57,0:52:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想带茜玻来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I long to bring Sybbie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.94,0:52:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定会喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.53,0:52:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这景色多美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.86,0:52:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不让你对生活充满感激吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you feel grateful we're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.08,0:52:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.33,0:52:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没想到自己还能再这样爱一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way I thought I'd never love again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.33,0:52:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.46,0:52:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这正好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.01,0:52:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧  这水...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we go back in? The water is...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.88,0:52:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看上去好幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They look very happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.09,0:52:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.05,0:53:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对茜玻  对他们都是天大的好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's thrilling for Sybbie, for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.35,0:53:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望汤姆和露西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like the idea of Tom and Lucy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.93,0:53:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年夏季都能在这里举办聚会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hosting a gathering here every summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.48,0:53:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到这成为家族传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until it becomes a family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.11,0:53:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳晒得我昏昏欲睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sun has made me sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.19,0:53:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪  我想在晚饭前打个盹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'll excuse me, I think I'll have a nap before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.74,0:53:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去也有点累\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look a little tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.70,0:53:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也去睡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.53,0:53:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我待会儿就去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.25,0:53:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说得对  您是看上去很累\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's right. You do look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.08,0:53:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来也没什么用吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never sure how helpful it is for people to point it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.50,0:53:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.51,0:53:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  你要一直写作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep writing, whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.30,0:53:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  如果您有烦恼  请说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mama, if something is troubling you, please just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.01,0:53:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没事  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, it's nothing, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.18,0:53:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不得不更改了晚餐桌的摆放\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've had to change the setting of the dinner table again,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.06,0:53:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们好像总算学会怎么给老爷熨衣服了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think they've got the hang of ironing His Lordship's shirts at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.44,0:53:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您该让我去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should've let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.82,0:53:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定很感激您的帮助  卡森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must be very grateful for your help, Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.32,0:53:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.15,0:53:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教他们做的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I showed them how to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.20,0:54:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很快很大声地用法语说了一堆话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they certainly spoke a lot of French very loud and very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.58,0:54:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情定下了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is anything settled yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.20,0:54:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别墅现在是茜玻小姐的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems the villa now belongs to Miss Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.21,0:54:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lucky girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.46,0:54:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你羡慕她吗  巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you envy her, Miss Baxter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.92,0:54:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信羡慕  贝茨先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not a big believer in envy, Mr. Bates.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.42,0:54:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.63,0:54:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有南法的别墅对我来说也无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I can live without a villa in the south of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.93,0:54:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么  巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want, Miss Baxter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.05,0:54:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了  卡森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come now, Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.68,0:54:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都知道巴克斯特小姐想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all know what Miss Baxter wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.22,0:54:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的爱恋可是坚定不移\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her affections are very firmly engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.68,0:54:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没"订"呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.77,0:54:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是还没订婚  但完全沉迷其中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not engaged in that way, perhaps, but thoroughly taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.77,0:54:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在说莫斯利先生吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we discussing Mr. Molesley?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.03,0:54:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.82,0:54:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果他一直没提出来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But suppose he never steps up to the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.61,0:54:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就做个老处女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I will be a spinster.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.82,0:54:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会嫁给别人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd never marry anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到他都花了那么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It took me long enough to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.37,0:54:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.00,0:54:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他考虑多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how long he's thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.80,0:54:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他查了日期后就确信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but once he checked the dates, he was sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.97,0:55:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生日正是在他们那段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was born exactly nine months after-- and I quote--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.10,0:55:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"诗意的短暂情缘"九个月后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the "idyllic interlude" they spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.47,0:55:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在我出生后不久就把别墅送给了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he gave her the villa soon after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.77,0:55:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定都是巧合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure that's all coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.69,0:55:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.31,0:55:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就能解释这个谜团了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would explain the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.85,0:55:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲非常爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father loved you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.15,0:55:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但罗斯孟德才长得像他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Rosamund's the one who looks like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.32,0:55:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望这能让您好受点  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope this helps, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.16,0:55:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  巴克斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Baxter.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.78,0:55:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.87,0:55:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that for? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.37,0:55:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有点烧心  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a bit of heartburn. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.83,0:55:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是事情传开了怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will happen if the story gets out, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.67,0:55:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡森肯定会递交辞呈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose Carson will hand in his notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.71,0:55:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.75,0:55:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我认识的最不法国的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the least French person I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.67,0:55:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不喜欢大蒜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't even like garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.92,0:55:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又不是板上钉钉的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not exactly cast-iron proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.10,0:55:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么这么快就准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How have they managed this so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.01,0:55:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就是金钱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because time is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.27,0:55:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的问题是  演员们要说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The problem now is what are the actors gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.27,0:55:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.19,0:55:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给他们写台词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I write the lines for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.65,0:55:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们并不总是按照台本来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but they don't always stick to the text,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.02,0:55:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们常常记不住演员们究竟说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and often we can't really remember what the actors have actually said.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.44,0:55:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如让莫斯利先生帮忙吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not let Mr. Molesley help?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.49,0:56:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  他能干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? What could he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.74,0:56:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是学校的老师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's the village schoolmaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.20,0:56:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他会读唇语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I know he can lip-read.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.41,0:56:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定能想到办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure he could sort something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.16,0:56:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.54,0:56:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他本来就每天都来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's been here every day as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.20,0:56:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们拍戏他都看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and watched all the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.83,0:56:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  巴伯先生  我准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, Mr. Barber. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.08,0:56:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把演员请出来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring on the thespians.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.34,0:56:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看上去真专业  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That looks very professional, milady,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您不介意我这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you don't mind my saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.97,0:56:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新速反相机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the new Speed Reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.64,0:56:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍照前能看到画面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can see the image before you take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.64,0:56:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还会想出什么来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, what will they think of next?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.73,0:56:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在楼下如何了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you getting on downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.27,0:56:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I think, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.94,0:56:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些法国人  他们很法国  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although, they're very French, the French, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.48,0:56:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是必然的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose they're bound to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.69,0:56:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.49,0:56:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor things.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.53,0:56:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样挺不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, this is pretty good,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.86,0:56:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卡森  可以把电话拿开吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, Carson, could you move the telephone?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.03,0:56:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点破坏画面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It spoils it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.49,0:56:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你工作得这么开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's lovely to see you enjoying your labors.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.04,0:56:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels good to have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.12,0:56:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重归现实世界吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Foothold in the real world again?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.00,0:56:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something like that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.96,0:57:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.96,0:57:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.30,0:57:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.93,0:57:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.23,0:57:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我当初年轻时  作为门童\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the Lady Grantham I first went to work for
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.81,0:57:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾服务过的格兰瑟姆夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a young hallboy wet behind the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.57,0:57:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.82,0:57:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.19,0:57:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  卡森  可以让我们单独待会儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Carson. Could you leave us for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.03,0:57:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.37,0:57:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"维奥莱特  我的爱"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Violette, mon adorée."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.37,0:57:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.63,0:57:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽有只小羊羔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary had a little lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.84,0:57:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的羊毛白似雪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its fleece was white as snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.92,0:57:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  斯特宾斯先生  准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, Mr. Stubbins, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.55,0:57:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能准备得更好了  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As ready as I can be, Mr. Barber,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.43,0:57:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我无法控制隔音和布景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I've not controlled the soundproofing or the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.43,0:57:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把德克斯特先生请过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we could have Mr. Dexter, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.77,0:57:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.64,0:57:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台词呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are the lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.39,0:57:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.52,0:57:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.44,0:58:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -站这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - And here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.03,0:58:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话要跟着电影的节奏来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, time your speech to match the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.24,0:58:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  别靠太近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no. Don't lean in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.53,0:58:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量保持头别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And try not to move your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.16,0:58:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.20,0:58:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇铃噤声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ring the bell for silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.50,0:58:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.04,0:58:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始录音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rolling sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.84,0:58:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是安小姐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Well, if it isn't Lady Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.85,0:58:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得你会找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I thought you might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.14,0:58:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现如今都没人会保密了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"No one can keep a secret these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.48,0:58:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我提醒你  我挥霍的是我的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"May I remind you it's my future to throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.94,0:58:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等  别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, wait. Don't go."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.36,0:58:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.79,0:58:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.87,0:58:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.46,0:59:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.76,0:59:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And action.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.85,0:59:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I knew where you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.93,0:59:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I only came to--"
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.73,0:59:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我在那里把头扭过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang on a minute. I turned me head round there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.44,0:59:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你...  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You... - Oh, y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.52,0:59:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写了这部分的台词  看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I've written a line to cover that. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.82,0:59:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来阻止你挥霍你的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I've only come to stop you throwing away your future."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.53,0:59:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说"未来"时扭头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You... y-you turn back on "future."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.20,0:59:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.49,0:59:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And action.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.58,0:59:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I knew where you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.46,0:59:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来阻止你挥霍你的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've only come to stop you throwing away your future."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.00,0:59:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大点声  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Louder, Miss Dalgleish!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.21,0:59:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能待在这里  眼看你毁了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I can't stay and watch you ruin yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.34,0:59:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我必须走  -停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Um, I must..." - Cut. Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.14,0:59:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  莫娜  等一下好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Myrna. Could I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.52,1:00:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.56,1:00:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特宾斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Stubbins?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.44,1:00:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来录音的  巴伯先生  不是来施展神迹的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I am here to record sound, Mr. Barber, not to perform miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.82,1:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可不是安·厄斯金小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Lady Anne Erskine she is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.90,1:00:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不能改改口音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couldn't she just learn the accent a bit better
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.61,1:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and do it again?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.90,1:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这口音很多人学一辈子都学不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People spend lives trying to learn this particular accent and failing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.70,1:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治·萧伯纳还为此写了部剧呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George Bernard Shaw wrote a play about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.24,1:00:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以做到  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you could do it, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.41,1:00:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德克斯特先生不就做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saw how Mr. Dexter managed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.29,1:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没那么难吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can't be that hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.71,1:00:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我不能  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But I couldn't. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.83,1:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会那口音吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You couldn't do the accent?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.13,1:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你会  你本来就会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you could. I think you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.25,1:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我不是演员  -莫娜算是演员吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But I'm not an actress. - Well, is Myrna an actress?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.17,1:00:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看她演《海达·高布乐》吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you keen to see her Hedda Gabler?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.05,1:00:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even so.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.05,1:00:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, just-just try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.55,1:00:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不行  那我们恐怕得彻底歇业了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can't do it, we'll shut down, possibly for good.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.97,1:00:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你行  我们就能继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can, you'll allow us to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.10,1:00:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.64,1:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do we deal with Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.60,1:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让她回楼上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, right now, um, get her back upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.19,1:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得知道这办法行不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to know if this is gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.36,1:00:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.61,1:00:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.62,1:01:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-台词给您  小姐  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here are the lines, milady. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.87,1:01:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道我怎么会干起这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how I get myself into these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.71,1:01:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I knew where you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.97,1:01:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来阻止你挥霍你的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I've only come to stop you throwing away your future.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.30,1:01:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能待在这里  眼看你毁了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I can't stay and watch you ruin yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.23,1:01:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.69,1:01:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cut.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.48,1:01:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起放一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Play them together.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.61,1:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是安小姐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if it isn't Lady Anne.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.70,1:01:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得你会找到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you might find me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.20,1:01:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现如今都没人会保密了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one can keep a secret these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.29,1:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew where you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.66,1:01:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来阻止你挥霍你的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've only come to stop you throwing away your future.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.13,1:01:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我提醒你  我挥霍的是我的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I remind you it's my future to throw away.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.92,1:01:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能待在这里  眼看你毁了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't stay and watch you ruin yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.01,1:01:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.68,1:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.01,1:02:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.16,1:02:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那最好是件道具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do hope that was a prop.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.08,1:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么时候画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was it painted?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.58,1:02:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她又为什么是他的"爱"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And why was she his adored one?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.66,1:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她为他献身了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because she granted the ultimate favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.58,1:02:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只相处了几日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were only together for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.58,1:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得可能吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does it sound likely?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.08,1:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就在九个月后出生只是个巧合吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's just a coincidence that Papa was born nine months later?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.46,1:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得  她回家后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I expect, when she got home,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.67,1:02:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爷爷见到她特别开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your grandpapa was jolly pleased to see her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.01,1:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  很显然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway, what's clear is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.55,1:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙米拉先生当时非常爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur de Montmirail was madly in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.10,1:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他什么时候结婚的  -我知道  我查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When did he marry? - Oh, I know that. I looked him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.56,1:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他1870年结婚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He married in 1870,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.06,1:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特出生五年后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}five years after Robert was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.14,1:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现任侯爵是1873年才出生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the present marquis arrived in 1873.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.90,1:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别墅算是送你奶奶的分手礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the villa was a sort of parting gift to your grandmother
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.52,1:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他就去找老婆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before he looked around for a wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.07,1:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.90,1:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Evidently.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.16,1:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要问问他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna sound him out.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.95,1:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对帕特莫太太怎么想  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- About Mrs. Patmore. - You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.16,1:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.91,1:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她有自己的房子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know she's got a house of her own.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.75,1:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她很孤单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know she's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.25,1:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我们都是条好出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a solution for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.92,1:03:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们像是在谋划什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look very conspiratorial.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.13,1:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在谈论帕特莫太太呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were talking about Mrs. Patmore
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.63,1:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有她是多喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how much she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.26,1:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does she indeed?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.05,1:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I like her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.51,1:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她是个好女人  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's a fine woman. - She is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.55,1:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有时担心她太孤单了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I worry sometimes that she's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.85,1:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有自己的农舍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's got her own cottage, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.31,1:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得她会想要个伴儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think she'd like some company in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.65,1:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么  但不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what you're thinking, but the answer's no.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.02,1:03:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直说你欣赏她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've always said you admired her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.94,1:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.11,1:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不能让个女人养活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I couldn't live off a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.40,1:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.70,1:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-哪怕她愿意吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Even if she wanted it? - Even then.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.53,1:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are things that are right
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.74,1:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there are things that are wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.28,1:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我无力改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I can't change that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.62,1:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for taking it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.38,1:03:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欠你个大人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe you a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.71,1:03:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is everything in order?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.84,1:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们给已经拍好的戏录好音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, once we've recorded sound for the scenes we've already shot,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.21,1:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得给剩下的内容写新本子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll need new material for what's left...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.26,1:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以说两句吗  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}M-May I have a word, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.51,1:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.56,1:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了所有如果电影是默片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I've been through all the dialogue cards
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.52,1:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会放映出来的对话卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that w-would've been shown if the picture were silent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.10,1:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是便开始编写\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I've started to sketch out scenes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.44,1:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能满足剧情需要的戏份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that would cover the needs of the plot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.36,1:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说你写了剧本吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean you've written a play?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.82,1:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少开始写了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I've started one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.94,1:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以给我看看吗  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Could I read these scenes? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.78,1:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你满意  我再继续写\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you're content, I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.62,1:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须按剧情梗概走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I bound by the plot synopsis?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.04,1:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如  她最终甩了他时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For instance, when she finally casts him off,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.12,1:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是安排一场浪漫的高潮戏更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}might it not be better with a big romantic climax?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.88,1:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.17,1:04:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔·本森就要把身家都丢在赌桌上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Bill Benson's about to throw away his life on the tables.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.42,1:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他空虚  孤独  毫无希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alone, hollow and without hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.10,1:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然  他抬起头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then suddenly he lifts his face
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.22,1:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到安就站在那里  高挑  平静  优雅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sees Anne standing there, tall, serene, graceful,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.27,1:04:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她眼里饱含泪水  闪闪发亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}her eyes shining with unshed tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.98,1:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一个冲动  把钱都揽了回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On an impulse, he snatches back his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.15,1:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止下注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rien ne va plus!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.32,1:05:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮盘旋转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The wheel spins.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.58,1:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他原本会输掉一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every last thing he owns would have gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.08,1:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.88,1:05:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的爱和美拯救了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her love, her beauty have saved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.38,1:05:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她握起他的手  他们离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She takes his hand, and they walk away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.72,1:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起退场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.26,1:05:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The end.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.77,1:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要哭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.43,1:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯利先生  请按你的心意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Molesley, please finish the script
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.31,1:05:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成剧本  然后拿给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}however you think best and bring it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.52,1:05:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.19,1:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你说他以前在这里工作吗  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You say he used to work here? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.32,1:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个男仆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was a footman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.20,1:05:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们并不知他还有隐藏的才华\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we weren't aware of his hidden talents.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.50,1:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的卡森  他这身厚衣服肯定热死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor Carson. He must be cooking in those heavy clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.46,1:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有轻便点的衣服可以给他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't there a lighter version he could wear?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.96,1:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-应该有  -谢谢  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I believe so. - Thank you, monsieur,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.05,1:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们英国人是不会嫌穿对的衣服太热的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we English are never too hot to wear the correct attire.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.55,1:06:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天请了些朋友来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've invited some friends tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.93,1:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们道别  并介绍你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to say goodbye and introduce all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.05,1:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的管家让我意识到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the presence of your butler reminds me
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.81,1:06:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在是你们的客人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we are now your guests
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.76,1:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该请求你们的准许\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I should have asked your permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.35,1:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.77,1:06:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们为你幸运的外孙女茜玻·布兰森举杯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us drink to your fortunate granddaughter, Sybil Branson.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.56,1:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-敬茜玻  -茜玻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To Sybbie. - Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.65,1:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是在就好了  我真想见见她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish she were here. I should like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.78,1:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你有天能见到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you will one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.90,1:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a lovely girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.03,1:06:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴听到一位继母这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nice to hear a stepmother talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.78,1:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对事情的发展很满意吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be pleased the way things have turned out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.99,1:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你爱的人被幸运眷顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When people you love have a stroke of luck,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.53,1:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直比自己走运还美妙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's almost better than being lucky yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.20,1:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但也不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.79,1:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.50,1:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书房里的那些小画像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know the miniatures in the library?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.84,1:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有一副是奶奶的  侧面还刻了字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of them is of Granny, and it's engraved on the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.89,1:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.35,1:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我半个多世纪以来都不得不看到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been obliged to see it there for more than half a century.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.06,1:07:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他不许我动它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he forbade me to move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.61,1:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还逼我起誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He made me swear.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.78,1:07:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有塔伯特先生的新消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any more news from Mr. Talbot?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.91,1:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我给你看过的电报后就没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not since the cable I showed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.07,1:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您很想他吧  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be missing him, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.91,1:07:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望他也想我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hope he misses me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.29,1:07:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷很快就会回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His Lordship will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.17,1:07:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他恐怕要震惊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid he'll be in for a shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.96,1:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢看电影拍摄吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you enjoyed the filming?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.09,1:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还算喜欢吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.09,1:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢巴伯先生和德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like Mr. Barber and Mr. Dexter
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.42,1:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也喜欢看电影的拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and watching how a film is made, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.76,1:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有点失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel a bit let down, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.06,1:07:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为达格利什小姐吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.51,1:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去很蠢  但\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It sounds stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.73,1:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我们能成为朋友呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we might become friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.27,1:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说见到你最喜欢的明星可能是个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say it can be a mistake to meet your favorite stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.94,1:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次算是说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this case, they'd be right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.32,1:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*疯狂韵律  门在那里*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Crazy rhythm, here's the doorway*
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.82,1:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我走我的  你走你的*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*I go my way, you go your way...*
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.70,1:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.00,1:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you feeling happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.50,1:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但还得辛苦一番呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am, but there's work to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.42,1:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是辛苦  你就越开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the more hard work involved, the happier you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.13,1:08:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know me already.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.96,1:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我想享受茜玻的好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, yes, I mean to enjoy Sybbie's good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.42,1:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我们都能享受其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want us all to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.51,1:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.05,1:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你算是成功地改变了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a leopard who has successfully changed his spots.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.89,1:08:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*疯狂韵律  我也发了疯*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Crazy rhythm, I've gone crazy, too...*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.06,1:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*疯狂韵律  我也发了疯*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Crazy rhythm, I've gone crazy, too.*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.69,1:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它太快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, he's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.53,1:08:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-再来  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Another one. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.36,1:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the ball?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.07,1:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它跑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.87,1:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, good hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.74,1:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.04,1:08:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治该去上床了  至少该准备了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George should be in bed, or at least on his way there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.71,1:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有别的孩子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have other children?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.67,1:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟第二任丈夫生的女儿  卡罗琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A daughter, Caroline, with my second husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.30,1:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治的父亲七年前死于了一场车祸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}George's father was killed in a car accident seven years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.67,1:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在乔治出生那天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the day George was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.09,1:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他抱过了宝宝  然后死在了回家的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He held the baby in his arms and died on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.30,1:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.06,1:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.98,1:09:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was perfect, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.02,1:09:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像童话里的王子一样帅气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As handsome as a prince in a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.86,1:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正直  坚强  很有梦想  也有责任心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moral, strong, full of dreams, determined to do his bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.53,1:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想他吗  -当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you miss him? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.03,1:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有时会想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although I sometimes wonder
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.03,1:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他还活着  会变成什么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what life would've made of him if he'd lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.04,1:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在有些地方...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.12,1:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a way?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.67,1:09:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想说  你有点让我想起了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was going to say, in a way, you remind me of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.50,1:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我说不上来为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although I couldn't tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.05,1:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.59,1:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现任丈夫呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about your present husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.42,1:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨利要务实得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Henry's much more pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.51,1:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不做梦  而是实干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are no dreams about him. He's a doer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.39,1:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总是没日没夜地测试自己的忍耐力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he must test his powers of endurance from morning till night.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.27,1:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他是个好搭档\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's a good workmate.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.93,1:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也帅吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is he handsome, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.48,1:09:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.69,1:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢帅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like them handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.77,1:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但天堂也有烦恼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's trouble in paradise?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.94,1:09:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need me to tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.20,1:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚姻是小说  不是短篇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that marriage is a novel, not a short story.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.32,1:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路上有各种情节转折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Full of plot twists along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.33,1:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想最终还是要看你爱不爱他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suppose it comes down to whether or not you love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.41,1:10:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.33,1:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为你是拍电影的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this because you work in the films?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.63,1:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我今晚说得太多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I've said more than enough for one evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.67,1:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家热情地欢迎别墅的继承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I hope you will warmly welcome our successors of the villa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.51,1:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟布兰森夫妇站在一起的是格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with the Bransons, perhaps you'll see Lord Grantham,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.10,1:10:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我现在可以称他为我的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whom I think I may now call my...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.72,1:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的好友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.48,1:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祝福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take them to your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.61,1:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*有些忧郁*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*There are blues*
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.74,1:10:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*来自你的担心*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*That you get from worry*
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.70,1:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*有些忧郁*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*There are blues*
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.91,1:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*来自你的痛苦*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*That you get from pain...*
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.12,1:10:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他处理得真得体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's handled it all with such good manners.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.41,1:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他觉得我是他哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he thinks I'm his brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.33,1:10:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚还以为他会说出来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a second there, I thought he was going to say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.21,1:10:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么说  你父亲很爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't talk like that. Your father loved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.50,1:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-够了  -但这并不够  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Enough. - But it's not enough, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.04,1:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这辈子可能都是个骗局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not when I might be a lifelong fraud.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.55,1:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个法国人的私生子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Frenchman's bastard
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.88,1:10:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篡夺了正当继承人的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who usurped the role of the proper heir.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.51,1:11:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但正当继承人就是马修的父亲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that would've been Matthew's father,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.05,1:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而马修的儿子即将继承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now Matthew's son will inherit,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.85,1:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以长远来看  也没区别嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so what difference does it make in the long run?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.76,1:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我心里无声的忧郁*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*The silent blues that's on my mind*
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.43,1:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*它们最凶狠了*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*They're the very meanest kind*
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.94,1:11:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我坏坏的爱人让我忧郁*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*The blues my naughty sweetie gives to me...*
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.65,1:11:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸可能是个冒牌货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid it's a real blow for Papa
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.53,1:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让他深受打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to find he may be an impostor.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.99,1:11:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的  他会心碎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it's true, he'll be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.41,1:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maman.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.66,1:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你在这里工作很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I've enjoyed watching you work out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.41,1:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎看到了你缺失的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a sort of flash of what you've been missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像还没准备好告别我的那部分生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems I'm not quite ready to say goodbye to that side of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.17,1:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了那幅小画像  赫克瑟姆夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've looked at the miniature, Lady Hexham,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.96,1:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and, uh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.21,1:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事就这么定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The matter is settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.92,1:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿回去给你奶奶吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please take it home for your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.05,1:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.84,1:11:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.47,1:11:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华  你疯了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Edouard, you're losing your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.60,1:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都过去那么久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this happened so long ago
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.93,1:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生在他认识你之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before he met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.23,1:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们该尊重他的遗愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel we should honour his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.16,1:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.20,1:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.25,1:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管您藏着什么秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever your secret may be,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.54,1:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就告诉爸爸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}isn't it a good time to share it with Papa?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.68,1:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真的不能跟海比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it's nothing compared to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.23,1:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是很美  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That was beautiful. - It was...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.31,1:12:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的很慷慨  但我们该回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been so gracious, but it's time for us to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.52,1:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快也要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be gone, too, before long.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.32,1:12:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道  房子里的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you know, the contents of the house
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.49,1:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是你母亲的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}already belong to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.78,1:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们需要拿走什么就请便吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you must take whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.66,1:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  他的遗嘱很明确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. His wishes are clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.70,1:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不理解你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.91,1:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要失去别墅了  还不够吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to lose the villa, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.08,1:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是要失去别墅  是要把它给我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not losing it. We're transferring it to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.20,1:12:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么喊他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't call him that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.71,1:12:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交给律师们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, our lawyers can manage the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.54,1:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很晚了  但我们去散散步吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it's late, but can we go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.92,1:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.09,1:13:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我们欠你的人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur, we are in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.09,1:13:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.88,1:13:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-夫人  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Madame. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.02,1:13:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让我开心吗  你的好父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And did he please me? Your blessed father?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.23,1:13:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.23,1:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得我该被如此对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe this is what I deserve.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.11,1:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我忧郁吗*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Am I blue?*
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.61,1:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我忧郁吗*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Am I blue?*
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.33,1:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我眼中不是泪吗*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Ain't these tears in my eyes*
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.13,1:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*在向你诉说*\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}*Tellin' you...*
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.84,1:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前怎么没跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you tell me before?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.46,1:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本打算说的  可我们突然要来这儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was going to, and then suddenly we were coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.63,1:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就不该来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you should never have come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.55,1:13:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得给你找个好医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to get you to a proper doctor,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.97,1:13:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不能是马赛的庸医\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't mean some quack in Marseilles.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.51,1:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉克森医生完全能够做出诊断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Clarkson is more than capable of coming up with a diagnosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.89,1:13:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们去伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we'll go to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.97,1:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有必要  可以去美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll-we'll go to America if we have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.23,1:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我们掌握更多情况再商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll discuss it when we know more.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.77,1:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have told me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.15,1:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是疾病夺走我们的生活前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the chance of a last treat
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.27,1:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次享受的机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before illness took over our lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.90,1:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能不至于呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It may not be as bad as that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.19,1:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特  我经营医院多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert, I've run the hospital for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.65,1:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我什么都没听到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think I just sat there with my ears blocked?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.24,1:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.90,1:14:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.66,1:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点也不想这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not what I wanted at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.62,1:14:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是可怜人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not sad people.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.99,1:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在病了我们也不可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My being ill now doesn't make us sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.71,1:14:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God. Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.50,1:14:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了母亲和身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To lose my mother and my name.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.34,1:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还要失去你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Must I lose you, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.30,1:14:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我受不了  -如果我能承受  你也能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't bear it. - If I can bear it, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.05,1:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了  我从一开始就爱上了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember, I loved you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.22,1:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你爱我前就爱上了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I loved you before you loved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.64,1:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一直让我羞愧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've always been ashamed of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.35,1:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必  我有钱  而你需要钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be. I had money. You needed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.85,1:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们有了爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then love came.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.31,1:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直很幸福  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we have been happy, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.90,1:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.86,1:14:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.99,1:14:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.24,1:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我还能再做一阵你的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I hope I can be everything for a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.92,1:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.04,1:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天还要早点动身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we must make an early start tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.46,1:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早该去睡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's hours past my bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.88,1:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.47,1:15:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我们还能买到蓝色列车的票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hope we can still get tickets on the Blue Train.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.51,1:15:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.54,1:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影机为什么放在了有软垫的隔间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is the camera in a padded cell?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.17,1:15:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会以为它是疯子呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone would think it was a lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.96,1:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的确变化多端\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's certainly unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.38,1:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克风绝不能收录任何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The microphone must not pick up any noise
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.38,1:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未经我准许的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless I have approved it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.26,1:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软垫间能盖住摄像机转动的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The padded box contains the sound of the camera working.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.31,1:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们得听你的了  斯特宾斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we're really in your hands now, Mr. Stubbins.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.89,1:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你说的  不是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your words, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.85,1:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.98,1:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go for a take. And...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.85,1:16:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意麦克风在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, please be aware of where the microphones are
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.02,1:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话要清晰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and speak clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.11,1:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次  莫娜  只表演  别说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, uh, this time, Myrna, mime but don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.03,1:16:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一个字别说  明白吗  -我不蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not a word. Do you understand? - I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.87,1:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只想听玛丽小姐说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We only want to hear Lady Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.12,1:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.66,1:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.62,1:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特  场记板准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, Albert, you ready with the clapstick?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.83,1:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇铃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ring the bell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.08,1:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roll the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.05,1:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Albert.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.13,1:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.26,1:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...action.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.34,1:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  先生  请下注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame, Messieurs, placez vos paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.10,1:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.60,1:16:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.15,1:16:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I always come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.56,1:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉  -停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sorry. - Cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.61,1:16:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.19,1:16:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家归位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, everyone, back to ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.49,1:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roll the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.78,1:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备  开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And... action.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.28,1:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  先生  请下注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame, Messieurs, placez vos paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.96,1:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.37,1:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.83,1:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I always come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.34,1:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉  -停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sorry! - Cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.29,1:17:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太难为我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's just very difficult for me
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.63,1:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的声音那么近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because she's right in me ear!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.92,1:17:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要从树丛里走出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you've got me coming out a bush!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.38,1:17:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  重来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. Reset please.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.59,1:17:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.80,1:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.26,1:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I always come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.06,1:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老天爷  -不用骂人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bloody hell! - There's no need to swear, is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.81,1:17:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-莫娜  抱歉  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Myrna, I- I'm sorry. I'm sorry. - Right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.89,1:17:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我受够了  -莫娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've had enough. - Myrna.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.94,1:17:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take your hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.77,1:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让开  -莫娜  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get out of my way! - Myrna, darling!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.10,1:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.36,1:17:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.99,1:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就知道她是个麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew she'd be trouble right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.03,1:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她粗鲁无礼  脾气还坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's rude. She's surly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.74,1:17:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但她现在还觉得很丢人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True, but now she also feels humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.33,1:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她动嘴  出来的却是玛丽小姐的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moving her mouth while Lady Mary's voice comes out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.91,1:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是她第一部有声片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is her first sound film.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.08,1:17:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今后怎么办啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happens to her next?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.41,1:17:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的事业大概是完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose her career's finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.12,1:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很多人都要完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose a lot of them are finished.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.96,1:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是  她得继续工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The point is they've got to get her back to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.38,1:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她不肯怎么办  他们又不能逼她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what if she won't come? They can't force her.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.47,1:17:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you two have a go?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.63,1:17:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道怎么跟她讲道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how to reason with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.01,1:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.02,1:18:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫娜  亲爱的  请下来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Myrna, darling, please come down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.52,1:18:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有你就拍不了戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't do anything without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.52,1:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有我还能说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can talk without me!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.31,1:18:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.90,1:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.28,1:18:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不如让女仆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it would be a good idea to let the maids
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.41,1:18:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去试试安抚她  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}see if they can make her comfortable, Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.95,1:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. If you think so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.12,1:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都退后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand back, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.54,1:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我们进去  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please let us in, Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.00,1:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能理解你的困境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We understand what you're going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.63,1:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们说的是真话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's true, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.84,1:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会下去任由他们羞辱  嘲笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going down just so they can humiliate me and laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.86,1:18:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.56,1:18:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真该听到他们每次首映时都怎么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should've heard them at every premiere.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.89,1:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"别说话  别张嘴"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Don't speak. Don't open your mouth."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.68,1:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们鄙视我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They despise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.23,1:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么不学学演说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you take elocution lessons?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.81,1:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人都在学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lots of people do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.81,1:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过  但我学不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I tried. I couldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.40,1:18:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都抓不到诀窍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Couldn't get the knack.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.77,1:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从你来到这里  就在为什么事生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's upset you since the day you got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.69,1:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是什么  -就是这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is it? - It's this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.95,1:18:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一看到《爵士歌手》就知道自己完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew I was finished the moment I saw The Jazz Singer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.99,1:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一把悬在我头上的剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been like a sword hanging over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.99,1:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为自己还能再拍几部戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought maybe I had a few more films ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.66,1:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这部就是我的最后一部了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this one will be me last.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.08,1:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可未必\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.12,1:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到的那些片段里你挺不错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look good in the bits I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.54,1:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我的声音呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how do I sound, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.00,1:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实就是  像美国人说的  我过气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the fact is I'm washed up, as the Yanks say.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.50,1:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是明日黄花了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm yesterday's news.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.76,1:19:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了  大小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.42,1:19:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里又不是你的影迷俱乐部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not talking to your fan club now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.55,1:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.26,1:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有名  美丽  还有钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're famous, beautiful and rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.43,1:19:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便你的电影事业结束了又如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what if your film career is over?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.68,1:19:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能做很多事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's any number of things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.18,1:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, dust yourself off.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.77,1:19:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便  对服务你的人态度好点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And while you're at it, try being polite to the people who serve you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.48,1:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  黛西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.98,1:19:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我们的一员  不是他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're one of us, not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.36,1:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just remember it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.53,1:19:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.53,1:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整理一下  我们该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Straighten your hair, and let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.16,1:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.53,1:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她快好了  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's almost ready, Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.83,1:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吧  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are, aren't you, Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.88,1:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前有个妹妹跟你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a sister just like you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.05,1:19:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.38,1:20:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.84,1:20:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我想到了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remind me of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.39,1:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她1919年因西班牙流感而死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She died of the Spanish flu in 1919.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.52,1:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为我们家不会有事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't think it would touch our family,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.77,1:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可天不遂人愿啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you never know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.06,1:20:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.62,1:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.33,1:20:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我来说值得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're worth it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.29,1:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止下注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rien ne va plus.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.22,1:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你是我的救星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It seems you're my savior.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.22,1:20:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备今后还要长长久久地做你的救星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I intend to remain your savior for a very long time to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.35,1:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mary?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.31,1:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.60,1:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.52,1:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.94,1:21:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您让他们知道规矩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you put them to rights?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.48,1:21:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我可以这么说  不会有人反驳的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I can say so without fear of contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.95,1:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他们明确地知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left them in no doubt as to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.32,1:21:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么才叫妥当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how things are done when they are done properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.91,1:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  贝茨先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eh, Mr. Bates?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.78,1:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说得非常明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you made your feelings clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.20,1:21:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们绝对是知道英国管家有多不好惹了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They certainly know what it is to deal with an English butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.33,1:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拿衣服吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, get your coats.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.08,1:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你时  我想到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watching you, it took me back to the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.13,1:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个以前在阁楼上演的戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}plays you three used to put on in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.63,1:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过这次事关要更重大些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except there's rather more riding on it this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.80,1:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无意挑刺  可我们怎么知道她能行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't mean to be harsh, but how do we know she's any good?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.51,1:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, she's absolutely superb.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.72,1:21:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把爸爸的电报给奶奶看了  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I showed Granny Papa's telegram, Tom,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.18,1:21:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你该去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you ought to look in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.64,1:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we should go up now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.10,1:21:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.60,1:21:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该由你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It ought to be you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.81,1:21:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把小画像交给她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can give her the miniature.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.11,1:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么小画像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What miniature is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.36,1:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来话长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.16,1:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有声片对于西区剧院的演员肯定是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talkies must be good news for the actors in the West End theaters.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.62,1:21:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他们是好事  对我是坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good news for them, bad news for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.08,1:21:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克风致死  是吧  盖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Death by microphone, eh, Guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.37,1:21:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这行本就是赌运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our business has always been a game of chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.79,1:22:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.01,1:22:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个主意  达格利什小姐  或许能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have an idea, Miss Dalgleish, which might just help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.89,1:22:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天一早就带你妈妈去医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm taking your mama to the hospital first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.18,1:22:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm dreading it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.22,1:22:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这话能说给你听  不能说给她听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's for you to hear, not her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.64,1:22:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为他们会抵抗一番呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought they might put up more of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.19,1:22:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也以为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So did we.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.36,1:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那母亲是想抵抗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mother wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.65,1:22:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后伊迪丝发现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then Edith found this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.07,1:22:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侧面刻了您的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's inscribed to you on the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.87,1:22:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.71,1:22:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们大概以为我们之间有什么越轨的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose they think something improper went on between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.26,1:22:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-大家都这么想吧  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I suppose everyone does. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.30,1:22:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会那么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.72,1:22:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真不会撒谎  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're such a bad liar, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.93,1:22:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要像你那么不会撒谎肯定寸步难行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd never have got anywhere if I were as rotten a liar as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.98,1:23:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会尽量每年都在别墅相见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're going to try and meet at the villa every year.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.73,1:23:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人  一起度夏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole family together, in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.98,1:23:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不热吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Won't it be too hot?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.90,1:23:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们希望您可以去试试看  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We hope you'll come and find out. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.16,1:23:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.12,1:23:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早过了那年纪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's-that's all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.41,1:23:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.12,1:23:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴认识了你  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am happy to have known you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.75,1:23:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最终相处得还不错  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we got on pretty well in the end, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.88,1:23:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.21,1:23:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.46,1:23:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是我们希望茜玻嫁的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You weren't quite what we had in mind for Sybil,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.51,1:23:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们都接受了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we got past it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.34,1:23:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活不就是这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.97,1:23:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受始料未及的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Getting past the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.51,1:23:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许从中吸取教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And perhaps learning from it,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.68,1:23:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which I think we can say we've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.56,1:23:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这些年是我的好朋友  维奥莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been a good friend to me through the years, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.31,1:23:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我也是您的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope I've been a friend to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.27,1:23:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你也有家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now you're settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.48,1:23:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫德回归了家族  大家都高兴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maud's back in the family, and everyone's happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.78,1:23:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小画像是什么时候画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the miniature painted?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.16,1:23:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还做模特了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you sit for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.91,1:24:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我们有天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we... we went for a walk
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.46,1:24:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去城里散步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the town one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.42,1:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有家店铺里  有个男人在拍照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there was a shop where a man was taking photographs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.71,1:24:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得很清楚  因为他是我见过的第一个摄影师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I remember 'cause he was the first photographer I'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.59,1:24:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定是照那个画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must have copied it from that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.89,1:24:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙米拉把它给我寄到了伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Montmirail sent it to me in London
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.85,1:24:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还附了一封胡言乱语的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a silly scribbled letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.85,1:24:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把它寄了回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sent it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.60,1:24:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我该把它烧掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, I should have burned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.56,1:24:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不打扰您休息了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll leave you to rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.02,1:24:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们想说  我们非常感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we wanted to say how very grateful we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.44,1:24:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜玻也会感激的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Sybbie will be, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.32,1:24:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里很美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.74,1:24:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.26,1:24:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该上床了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time for bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.55,1:24:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我把这些收拾一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'll just tidy these up.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.39,1:25:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.77,1:25:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙米拉先生的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The letters of Monsieur de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.73,1:25:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都标注了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're clearly labeled?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.27,1:25:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.57,1:25:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她说她什么都不记得了是在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So she was lying when she said she remembers nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.94,1:25:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒谎"有点重了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Lying" is a harsh word.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.20,1:25:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许她是选择遗忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe she pushed it to the back of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.99,1:25:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在闹成这样  恐怕又回忆起来了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't believe it stayed there with all the fuss going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.45,1:25:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我去见她时再问她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll ask when I go and see her.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.60,1:25:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴罗先生在这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this the way to find Mr. Barrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.19,1:25:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往左走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Left.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.19,1:25:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就藏在这里啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So this is where you hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.70,1:25:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我帮什么忙吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I help with anything, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.61,1:25:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以帮个忙  别再喊我"先生"了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you can certainly help by not calling me "Sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.20,1:26:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道卡森先生会怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure what Mr. Carson would make of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.66,1:26:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接待一位来自楼上的客人  德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my receiving a visit from an upstairs guest, Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.50,1:26:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡森先生现在又不管事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Mr. Carson isn't in charge now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.79,1:26:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是管事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.84,1:26:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有人进来呢  会怎么说啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suppose someone comes in. What would they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.30,1:26:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.67,1:26:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在美国住了十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've lived in America for ten years now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.05,1:26:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信那一套了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe in that stuff anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.85,1:26:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请喊我盖吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, call me Guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.35,1:26:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本名叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.52,1:26:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昆丁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quentin.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.73,1:26:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昆丁·赛博姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quentin Sidebotham.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.03,1:26:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was a good decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.78,1:26:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你接下来打算怎么办吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what you're doing next?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.49,1:26:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think anybody does.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.53,1:26:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得回家  等待事态发展了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shall go home and await developments.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.45,1:26:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能会联系克里夫·布洛克或查理·卓别林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might call Clive Brook or Charlie Chaplin,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.21,1:26:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问他们怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}see what they think.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.12,1:26:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识查理·卓别林啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know Charlie Chaplin?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.33,1:26:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他有点疯  但我是认识他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's a little wild for me, but yeah, I-I know him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.17,1:26:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好莱坞的名声有些差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hollywood gets some bad publicity,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.67,1:26:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我住在汉考克公园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I live in a place called Hancock Park,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.72,1:26:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里挺不错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's... it's pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.26,1:27:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.68,1:27:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不自己来看看呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, why don't you come and see for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.52,1:27:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.61,1:27:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.53,1:27:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作要经常出行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I travel a lot for my work,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.03,1:27:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有妻子照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't have a wife to look after me, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.70,1:27:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.91,1:27:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做你的贴身男仆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be your valet?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.04,1:27:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.29,1:27:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打理家里  安排我们的行程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd run the house and organize our journeys,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.17,1:27:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我过得舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}make me comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.38,1:27:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们都过得舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make us both comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.17,1:27:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  如果我的事业完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, if my career folds,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.34,1:27:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就得另做打算了  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we'd have to think again, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.72,1:27:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的事业不会完的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your career won't fold.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.72,1:27:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.76,1:27:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.52,1:27:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你想好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You let me know when you've...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.10,1:27:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come to a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.70,1:28:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我都检查好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. I have everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.49,1:28:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等结果一出来  我会立刻送过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will come up to the house with the results as soon as I have them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.58,1:28:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你觉得乐观吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But do you feel optimistic?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.58,1:28:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特  这种话没有意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert, there's no point in that sort of talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.71,1:28:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰瑟姆夫人太懂行了  我没法糊弄她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lady Grantham knows too much to pull the wool over her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.46,1:28:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即便真的糟得不能再糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But even if everything is as bad as it could be,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.59,1:28:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以手术吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's still a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.96,1:28:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一步步来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's take it one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.51,1:28:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.76,1:28:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特不明白  但其实还可能更糟呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert doesn't see it, but things could be a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.51,1:28:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少人面对这种情况时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many have to face this kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.89,1:28:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己虚度了人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}feeling they've wasted their lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.85,1:28:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.23,1:28:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.15,1:28:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农场的情况怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are things at the farm?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.78,1:28:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥挤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cramped.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.28,1:28:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的梅森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.45,1:28:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要是听到你这么说会很难过的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd be so unhappy to hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.82,1:28:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他近来总提起你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been talking about you lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.12,1:28:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.45,1:28:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你是个好女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saying what a fine woman you are
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.33,1:28:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很欣赏你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and how much he admires you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.41,1:28:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does he? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.42,1:28:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他不愿更进一步了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he won't take it any further.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.42,1:28:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.79,1:29:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不能请你搬去农场住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he can't ask you to live at the farm
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.51,1:29:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又不愿让个女人养活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he couldn't be dependent on a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.72,1:29:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, couldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.47,1:29:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走着瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.31,1:29:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我们找到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look what we've found.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.48,1:29:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我翻维奥莱特的东西时发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was going through Violet's things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.15,1:29:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"蒙米拉侯爵的信件"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The letters of the Marquis de Montmirail."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.48,1:29:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.36,1:29:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对爸爸来说不是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't look good for Papa
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.40,1:29:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她觉得有必要对此保密的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if she felt the need to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.49,1:29:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别急着下结论嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's not jump the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.15,1:29:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  你们在忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm so sorry. Are you in the middle of something?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.82,1:29:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.70,1:29:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以单独跟你说句话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could I speak to you alone for a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.33,1:29:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.58,1:29:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.91,1:29:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们可以一起看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I thought we could read them together.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.96,1:29:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯蒂  我们来看  然后把内容告诉大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bertie, you and I can do it and report back what they contain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.17,1:29:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再把消息告诉爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we'll break the news to Papa.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.51,1:29:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.97,1:29:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.26,1:29:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正准备拍最后一幕戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're just about to film our last set piece,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.64,1:29:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚宴戏  本森意识到他必须放弃她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the-the dinner when Benson realizes he must give her up
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.23,1:29:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后赶去了伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and rushes off to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.40,1:29:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我刚刚还在练呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I've just been learning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.98,1:30:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯利写得真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Molesley's done a wonderful job.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.52,1:30:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过  群演受够了没钱拿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you the extras were fed up with not being paid,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.32,1:30:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怪他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't blame them,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.78,1:30:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还在等钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm still waiting for the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.41,1:30:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会做什么太过分的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, they won't do anything too drastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.41,1:30:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Won't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.32,1:30:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说他们罢工了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say they're not coming into work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.04,1:30:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要怎么帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.41,1:30:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的仆人可以替他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could your servants stand in?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.92,1:30:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去问问他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're welcome to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.84,1:30:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗  巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there something else, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.51,1:30:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你  我根本完不成这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could never have got through any of this without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.02,1:30:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样  那我很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that's true, then I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.57,1:30:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吻你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.28,1:30:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.99,1:30:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you want to?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.03,1:30:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我这人太老派  我不认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I'm too old-fashioned to believe that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.33,1:30:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以只考虑自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what I want is the only thing that matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.71,1:31:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我冒犯你了吗  -完全没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Have I offended you? - Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.92,1:31:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于一个已婚的老女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing is nicer for an old married woman
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.34,1:31:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么比得知她仍令人心动更妙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than to find she's still an object of desire.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.30,1:31:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你丈夫回来  你最好别告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you better not tell your husband when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.09,1:31:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能会打我的鼻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might, uh, hit me on the nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.22,1:31:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那多让人激动啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm, wouldn't that be thrilling?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.77,1:31:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个帅气的男人为我争风吃醋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two gorgeous men fighting for my favors.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.56,1:31:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您按铃了  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You rang, milady?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.06,1:31:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她还留下了他的信  -看来是一封都没丢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So she'd kept his letters? - Seemingly. Every one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.19,1:31:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不问她想隐瞒什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't ask what she had to hide,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.99,1:31:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防你们告诉我答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in case you tell me the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.86,1:31:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分还挺哀伤的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, most of them are rather sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.32,1:31:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和他妻子显然并没什么感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was clearly no love lost between him and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.53,1:31:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但信里是怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what do they tell us about
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.49,1:31:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在法国的那段日子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the days they spent together in France?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.25,1:31:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他们那段日子里没通信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid that they didn't write to each other then.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.79,1:31:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们还是无法证明究竟发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we still have no proof of what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.04,1:31:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕谜题就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose that is where the mystery resides.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.00,1:31:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天来见维奥莱特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll come and see Violet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.63,1:31:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.80,1:31:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.55,1:31:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是律师所谓的"相关方"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're what the lawyers call "an interested party."
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.76,1:31:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.35,1:32:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说  我们可以跟达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean we'd be up there on the screen
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.02,1:32:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和德克斯特先生一起上大银幕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with Miss Dalgleish and Mr. Dexter?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.81,1:32:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.52,1:32:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是这样  -我乐意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's exactly what I mean. - Well, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.65,1:32:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡森先生也会乐意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm, so will Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.86,1:32:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯利先生也会想加入的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Molesley will want to join in.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.44,1:32:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你需要多少人  -十个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How many do you need? - Uh, we need ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.20,1:32:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹可小姐  你想去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Miss Denker, are you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.45,1:32:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.62,1:32:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要照顾老夫人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to keep an eye on Her Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.66,1:32:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那梅森先生呢  -我可以去问问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What about Mr. Mason? - I could always ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.37,1:32:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  现在就赶紧去农场问他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, hurry to the farm and ask him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.45,1:32:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有适合我们的戏服吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they've got costumes for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.66,1:32:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们需要时间改尺寸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, they'll need time to fit them,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.83,1:32:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们今天结束前得去一趟楼上服装部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so you should go upstairs to wardrobe before the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.50,1:32:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那仆人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about servants?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.42,1:32:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来服侍我们啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's going to wait on us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.34,1:32:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想  可以让艾伯特来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I was thinking we could use Albert.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.72,1:32:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能为达格利什小姐服务吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would I be serving Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.59,1:32:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以啊  -好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I suppose so. - Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.89,1:32:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  都回去工作吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, let's get back to work, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.01,1:32:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  走吧  -快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, come on now. - Come along.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.10,1:32:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍电影肯定是史上最慢的职业了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Filming must be the slowest occupation known to man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.15,1:32:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰川都显得不耐烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It makes a glacier look impatient.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.27,1:32:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特一定难受死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose Robert's in hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.61,1:32:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还指望着等他们回来时一切都结束了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was longing for it all to be over by the time they got back.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.57,1:32:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想  可以缓解他的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could ease his pain if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.95,1:32:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发现了蒙米拉先生的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found the letters of Monsieur de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.20,1:33:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但罗伯特仍没有得到他需要的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Robert still doesn't have the answer he needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.75,1:33:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会假装我没听懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't pretend not to understand you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.96,1:33:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟你说小画像的事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did they tell you about the miniature?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.04,1:33:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有什么意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's its significance?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.71,1:33:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拿来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, could you fetch it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.84,1:33:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在右边下面的抽屉里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in the bottom right-hand drawer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.76,1:33:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你打开后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you open it at the back,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.34,1:33:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会发现他附的那封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'll find the letter he sent with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.35,1:33:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年了  还在呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's still there after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.39,1:33:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以读出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.65,1:33:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"亲爱的维奥莱特  我们错过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Chère Violette, we have missed the chance
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.49,1:33:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受完美爱情的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to know perfect love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.91,1:33:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你肯改主意  我们还有机会"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we still can if you would only change your mind."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.08,1:33:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不直说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't you just tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.71,1:33:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was nothing to tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.71,1:33:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.09,1:33:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被纠缠了好多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apart from years of being pestered.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.42,1:33:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.84,1:33:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.01,1:33:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.55,1:34:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我再没见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never saw him after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.22,1:34:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我会受不了诱惑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew I'd have given in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.27,1:34:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我再经受考验  肯定会犯错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'd been tested again, I would have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.19,1:34:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时是个痴情的傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was a fool for love in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.44,1:34:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年后  我们去了俄国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few years later, we went to Russia,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.95,1:34:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又惹了大麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I got into terrible trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.78,1:34:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,险些吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I nearly did.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.41,1:34:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟克拉根亲王  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With Prince Kuragin. Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.33,1:34:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么避免在侯爵身上犯错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you avoid it with the marquis?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.58,1:34:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记不得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.42,1:34:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是我这辈子见过的最有魅力的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was the most attractive man I'd ever met in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.46,1:34:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我才结婚不久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I hadn't long been married,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.42,1:34:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是觉得破坏我的婚姻未免太可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it must have seemed a shame, you know, to spoil that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.59,1:34:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望你说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you'd said all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.01,1:34:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望你觉得我一辈子都过得很违心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't want you to think my life had been a fraud,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.60,1:34:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.02,1:34:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟罗伯特的父亲挺幸福的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was happy with Robert's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.52,1:34:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以英国人的方式足够幸福了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, happy enough in that English way,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.11,1:34:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么都不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when you never talk about anything
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.74,1:34:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是信任彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.95,1:35:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果克拉根和蒙米拉合体了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they'd put Kuragin and Montmirail together,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.99,1:35:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定会堕落成一个荡妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have come out as some sort of scarlet woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.16,1:35:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不觉得你浪荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't seem very scarlet to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.71,1:35:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要委托你确保人们不会这么想我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm trusting you to make sure that's not how I'm remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.76,1:35:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下任伯爵就是马修的儿子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the next earl will be Matthew's son,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.26,1:35:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孙子  你的曾孙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my grandson, your great-grandson.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.81,1:35:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力让他珍重你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll do my best to see he values you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.93,1:35:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.10,1:35:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我可以信任你做正确的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I can trust you to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.65,1:35:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's very generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.36,1:35:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们有过不少分歧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, because we've had our tussles, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.11,1:35:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是  但我很高兴你来到了唐顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's true, but I'm glad you came to Downton.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.41,1:35:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多年来  我都没有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd never known anyone whose opinion I could trust,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.04,1:35:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相信她总会做出正直判断的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you know, to be morally right, not for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.79,1:35:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我母亲死后就没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, not since my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.04,1:35:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定好奇我为什么让你整理我的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have wondered why I asked you to go through my papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.55,1:35:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did rather.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.13,1:36:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我想起很久以前的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I think about that world of long ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.72,1:36:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我还是个初次穿裙衬的姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I... I was a girl in my first crinoline...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.73,1:36:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些时刻  我好像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...in those moments, I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.52,1:36:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了另一个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as if I've been transported to a different planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.11,1:36:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so you have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.94,1:36:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个活得够久的人都会有这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like every human being who lives long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.49,1:36:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我的确活了够久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I have. Lived long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.29,1:36:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.55,1:36:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但我等不及了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, but I just couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.80,1:36:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.97,1:36:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.06,1:36:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是你父亲的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're your father's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.69,1:36:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能假装这没让我如释重负\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't pretend I'm not relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.90,1:36:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能假装这没让我觉得受辱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't pretend I'm not insulted.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.11,1:37:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这跟我的出生毫无关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you think he gave you the villa
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.99,1:37:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他为什么要把别墅送你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if it has nothing to do with my birth?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.61,1:37:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这跟你的出生很有关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it had everything to do with your birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.07,1:37:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的出生  让他明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you were born, it sent a message
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.04,1:37:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要的永远都不可能了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that what he wanted was never going to happen
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.08,1:37:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他该向前看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it was time to move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.62,1:37:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从未像爱您那样爱过他妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He never loved his wife as he loved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.38,1:37:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别墅就证明了这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The villa proves that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.96,1:37:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.88,1:37:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that's not for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.35,1:37:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嗯  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.94,1:37:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了最后一场戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked through the final scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.61,1:37:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.82,1:37:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样的工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does this kind of work appeal to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.11,1:37:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为电影写剧本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}writing plays for the screen?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.91,1:37:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you-you mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.08,1:37:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如一年四部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, say, four a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.83,1:37:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把我看好的书或短篇故事寄给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd send you the book or short story I was keen on
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.83,1:37:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写好注释和建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with my notes and suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.33,1:37:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千块的剧本我给你七百几尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, I would pay 700 guineas against a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.59,1:37:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.96,1:38:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.88,1:38:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你写剧本的酬劳是七百几尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, you'd get 700 for writing the script.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.17,1:38:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能拍成电影  会涨到一千几尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would rise to a thousand if the film is made.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.26,1:38:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每部剧本吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For each script?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.52,1:38:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.15,1:38:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这胸衣  我可不羡慕她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't envy her if these corsets are anything to go by.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.24,1:38:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真是荒唐  -开心点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is absurd. - Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.99,1:38:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟  你应该挺习惯这戏服的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all, you should be used to the costume.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.87,1:38:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在位置上摆了铭牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've put the names on the places,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.34,1:38:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  请找到自己的座位坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so, please, all of you, find your chair and sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.96,1:38:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡森先生  您扮演庞弗雷伯爵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, Mr. Carson, you will be playing Lord Pumphrey
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.21,1:38:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at the head of the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.92,1:38:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在这里感觉好怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems odd to be sitting in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.34,1:38:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里站过够久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've spent enough time standing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.22,1:38:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你想了够久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say you've spent long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.76,1:38:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧  德克斯特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may be right, Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.93,1:38:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  你的提议是我想的那个意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me, did your offer mean what I think it did?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.06,1:38:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么意思都随你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can mean as little or as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.73,1:39:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望有很深远的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like it to mean a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.61,1:39:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你走运了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.62,1:39:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-休斯太太  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mrs. Hughes. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.33,1:39:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.04,1:39:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都认不出你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.21,1:39:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.55,1:39:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, no, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.09,1:39:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当我们不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, we're not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.34,1:39:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵大人  请您到摄像机后面来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Lord, if-if you could make your way up behind the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.76,1:39:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.11,1:39:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看上去像个稻草人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I look like something to scare the crows.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.90,1:39:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.78,1:39:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直是优雅的典范\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a picture of elegance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.82,1:39:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐吧  来点热乎的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, sit down here and have something warming.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.95,1:39:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为都是上色的水呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought it were just colored water.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.83,1:39:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, so it is for the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.95,1:39:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给咱们偷带了点好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For us, I've smuggled in something nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.87,1:40:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  真不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you're right. This is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.79,1:40:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小两口看上去多登对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't the young couple look nice together?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.38,1:40:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮助他们感觉一定很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must be wonderful to feel you're helping them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.97,1:40:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想为他们做更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to do more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.59,1:40:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想跟你谈这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is what I want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.15,1:40:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不紧张吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not nervous?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.48,1:40:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, how should a man feel
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.94,1:40:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部成真时该有什么感觉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when all his dreams have come true?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.36,1:40:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部梦想吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All your dreams?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.95,1:40:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  是这样  巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I know, but, you see, Miss Baxter...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.24,1:40:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我菲丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phyllis.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.24,1:40:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phyllis.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.29,1:40:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.08,1:40:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本只能靠学校老师的薪水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The best I could offer was a poor life
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.46,1:40:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一个贫穷的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a schoolmaster's salary.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.17,1:40:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也乐意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd have taken it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.21,1:40:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在你不用委屈自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now you won't have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.76,1:40:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要写能拍成电影的剧本了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna write plays to be made into films.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.93,1:40:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给巴伯先生写吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.18,1:40:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Mr. Barber now,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.22,1:40:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我真有本事  谁知道今后会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but who knows what'll happen if I'm any good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.47,1:41:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今后都是有声片了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, it's gonna be talking films from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.68,1:41:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, what the blazes?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.60,1:41:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能挣钱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these will pay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.15,1:41:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这辈子第一次可以提供富贵的生活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the first time, I can offer a decent prosperous life.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.86,1:41:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供我们两个享受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.28,1:41:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.74,1:41:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不打算下跪吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you not going to kneel?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.33,1:41:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你要我下跪吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you want me to? - I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.25,1:41:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有下次了嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.17,1:41:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right then, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.55,1:41:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意嫁给我吗  巴克斯特小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you marry me, Miss Baxter?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.18,1:41:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说...菲丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, Phyllis.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.27,1:41:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.64,1:41:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很愿意  莫斯利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I jolly well will, Mr. Molesley.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.57,1:41:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.33,1:42:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好样的  -好样的  莫斯利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well done. - Well done, Mr. Molesley.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.54,1:42:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的  莫斯利先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Mr. Molesley.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.71,1:42:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家安静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Settle down, everyone, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.04,1:42:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来拍第一条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go for a first take.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.38,1:42:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.13,1:42:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴克斯愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barkis is willing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.84,1:42:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.01,1:42:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也愿意去我的小农舍住吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you'll be content to live in my little cottage?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.59,1:42:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你觉得那样不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you think it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.14,1:42:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然不觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I most certainly do not.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.47,1:42:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把农场交给年轻人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now the young ones can have the farm?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.35,1:42:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把租约交给他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll surrender the lease.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.06,1:42:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要为这喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well, I'll drink to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.02,1:42:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  各位  -记住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right, and if we can... - Remember!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.15,1:42:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吐字清晰  脑袋别动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clarity, diction and keep your heads still.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.07,1:42:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.19,1:42:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始摄影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roll the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.66,1:42:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And action.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.04,1:42:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.58,1:42:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.96,1:42:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.04,1:42:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然行  我必须走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can and I must.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.54,1:42:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我留下  亲爱的安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I stay, darling Anne,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.55,1:42:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只会毁了你  还有我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll destroy you along with myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.80,1:42:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看不出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.93,1:42:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以一起抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll fight it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.18,1:43:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.64,1:43:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我没用  是我不被接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the worthless one. I'm the exile.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.31,1:43:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我没救了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the lost soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.43,1:43:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.07,1:43:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔  等等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.94,1:43:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他伤了她的心啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's broken her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.53,1:43:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是个无赖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chap's a cad.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.40,1:43:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And cut.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.83,1:43:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.83,1:43:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.34,1:43:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊里的自助餐备好了  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The buffet in the hall is ready, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.38,1:43:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  巴罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Barrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.72,1:43:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  不知能不能跟您说件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady, I wonder if I might have a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.93,1:43:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.81,1:43:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想递交辞呈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to hand in my notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.40,1:43:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在这里并不是一直都很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know you haven't always been happy here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.77,1:43:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个  小姐  我在唐顿度过了美好时光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's not that, milady. I've had good years at Downton.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.44,1:43:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我建立了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I've formed a sort of--
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.15,1:44:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道该怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, I'm not sure what it is, really--
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.45,1:44:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟德克斯特先生建立了良好的友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a working friendship with Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.41,1:44:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-盖吗  -是的  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Guy? - That's it, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.54,1:44:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算结伴而行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we mean to travel together.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.79,1:44:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他拍电影  我照顾他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll make films, and I'll look after him.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.50,1:44:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按拍电影的人的话说  我做他的化妆师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be his dresser, as the film people put it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.13,1:44:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没想错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if I'm right...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.75,1:44:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最接近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then it's the nearest I've come to
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.13,1:44:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能诚实地生活的机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the offer of an honest way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.59,1:44:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要解释  巴罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't need to explain, Barrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.81,1:44:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祝福你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.68,1:44:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你在这残忍的世界里能尽量幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I hope you'll be as happy as our cruel world allows.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.19,1:44:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.99,1:44:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.37,1:44:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.08,1:44:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.84,1:44:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都在想你会不会怀念你的演艺事业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all wondering if you'll miss your acting career.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.96,1:44:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说会吧  然后来伦敦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, please say yes. Come up to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.38,1:45:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们给你找个角色  -不了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We'll find you a part. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.72,1:45:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是挺喜欢的  但一次就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've enjoyed it, in fact, but once will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.51,1:45:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要帮助吗  达格利什小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I help you, Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.06,1:45:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要点那火腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Um, I'd love some of that ham,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.93,1:45:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你够得到  再来点酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you can reach it, and a little sauce.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.15,1:45:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的声音怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's happened to your voice?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.69,1:45:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.57,1:45:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有那种难听的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you've lost the ghastly...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.36,1:45:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我并不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, I didn't mean "ghastly," exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.66,1:45:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很有天分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a natural.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.45,1:45:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格兰瑟姆夫人觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Lady Grantham thinks
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.53,1:45:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以去好莱坞当个美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can go to Hollywood and just be an American.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.33,1:45:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定能行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, why shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.62,1:45:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  伯蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come along, Bertie.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.75,1:45:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.58,1:45:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去趟楼下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, um, I just want to go downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.42,1:45:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.05,1:45:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么突然这么客气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is she so nice all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.88,1:45:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单  她不再害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's simple. She's not afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.43,1:45:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我完全为你疯狂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do know that I'm completely mad about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.47,1:45:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的巴伯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear Mr. Barber,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.02,1:45:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能答应你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.77,1:45:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可以说  我很喜欢跟你合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can say that I've loved working with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.32,1:46:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只能满足于此了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I must be content with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.28,1:46:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能得到这么多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all you're going to get.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.95,1:46:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸自己是我父亲的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm mainly glad to be my father's son
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.12,1:46:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要因为我爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.78,1:46:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说比血统更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It matters more to me than all the dynastic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.91,1:46:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so it should.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.75,1:46:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为茜玻高兴  只要她懂得要回馈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm happy for Sybbie, as long as she learns how to pay back.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.63,1:46:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢游手好闲的富人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't believe in the idle rich?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.21,1:46:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.38,1:46:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不希望我的家人是那样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want any member of my family to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.51,1:46:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.42,1:46:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去倒一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I'll have another cup.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.76,1:46:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.89,1:46:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也包括你未来的家人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that include any future member of your family?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.52,1:46:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  因为...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, yes, of course, becau...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.44,1:46:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还早  所以什么都别说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's early days, so don't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.86,1:46:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我什么都不会说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my darling, I won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.99,1:46:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想我可以吻你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I think that I can kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.37,1:46:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉克森医生来了  老爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Clarkson has arrived, milord.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.37,1:46:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我注意到你跟那位帅气的巴伯先生十分亲近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I notice you're very friendly with the handsome Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.37,1:46:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't start.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.42,1:47:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没惹麻烦  一直乖乖的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've kept myself out of trouble and I've been good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.84,1:47:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但的确忍得挺辛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With some difficulty, I might add.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.30,1:47:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是你担心的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is not what you were dreading.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.09,1:47:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶性贫血往往会被误诊为癌症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pernicious anemia is often mistaken for cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.55,1:47:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到几年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And until a few years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.14,1:47:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确可能会要了你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it might well have finished you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.31,1:47:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在有治疗办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there is now treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.57,1:47:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.44,1:47:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不会很舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't be particularly enjoyable,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.98,1:47:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你会好起来  你不会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you will get better and you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.48,1:47:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  克拉克森医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, thank you, Dr. Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.69,1:47:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you very, very, very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.61,1:47:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.49,1:47:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也进来吃点晚餐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you must come in and have some supper.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.62,1:47:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今晚上挺将就的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's very much catch-as-catch-can tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.87,1:47:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仆人们都当了把影星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the servants are film stars now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.75,1:47:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大概别指望他们会愿回去当仆人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt we'll ever get them back behind the green baize door.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.96,1:47:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, milord!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.33,1:47:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  快来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady! Come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.79,1:47:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.71,1:47:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.76,1:47:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.55,1:47:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个口音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talk in that voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.80,1:47:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想说  我非常感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wanna say how grateful I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.89,1:47:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在我需要的时候帮我振作了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You both licked me into shape when I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.31,1:47:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.31,1:47:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那你要去好莱坞了  -为什么不呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So you'll go to Hollywood now? -  Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.31,1:48:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也没有家人值得我留恋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've no family to hold me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.23,1:48:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我现在拍过有声片了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I've done a talkie now,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.19,1:48:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算是领先一步了  希望是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which puts me ahead of the race, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.19,1:48:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了你是谁和你的出身就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just don't forget who you are or where you've come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.11,1:48:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也别让它阻碍你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't let it hold you back either.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.36,1:48:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.57,1:48:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.12,1:48:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫人的状况在急转直下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Lady Grantham's sinking fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.42,1:48:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都在楼上陪她呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're upstairs with her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.00,1:48:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备点咖啡或更烈的东西  以防万一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get some coffee or something stronger just in case.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.64,1:48:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查理  你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.43,1:48:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李尔王怎么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did King Lear say?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.02,1:48:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"吹啊  大风  吹裂你的脸颊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Blow, winds, and crack your cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.52,1:48:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发作啊  吹啊  激流和狂飙"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rage, blow, you cataracts and hurricanoes."
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.19,1:48:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她离开的时刻终于到来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has the moment of her leaving come at last?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.24,1:49:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一位尊贵的夫人即将离世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That so great a lady should go
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.96,1:49:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里却有一堆拍电影的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the house is full of film people.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.10,1:49:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maud.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.01,1:49:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.31,1:49:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会相信的  但我会怀念你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you won't believe me, but I sh... I shall miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.52,1:49:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来确认我快不行了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or have you just come to check I'm on the way out?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.61,1:49:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您需要什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.90,1:49:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的  亲爱的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever I have wanted, dearest boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.62,1:49:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就给过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have given me long before now
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.95,1:49:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and many times over.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.91,1:49:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的妈妈  希望我没让您失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear Mama, I hope I haven't been a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.25,1:49:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一向比我聪明多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were always so much cleverer than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.46,1:49:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.55,1:49:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们现在别为了这个闹别扭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't let that come between us now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.55,1:50:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可比我这辈子善良多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are far kinder than I have ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.35,1:50:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯拉  我欠你个道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cora, I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.35,1:50:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到你能撑下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't think you'd last the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.11,1:50:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.40,1:50:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.69,1:50:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以前可没听我说过这种话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that's something you haven't heard me say until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.16,1:50:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话值得等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was worth waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.12,1:50:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的玛丽  还有伊迪丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Mary dear and Edith.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.54,1:50:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是好孙女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've been wonderful granddaughters.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.46,1:50:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开你们时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I leave you both
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.54,1:50:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚信你们一生都会幸福丰富\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}confident that your lives will be happy and fruitful.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.55,1:50:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.18,1:50:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的奶奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darling Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.26,1:50:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, that must be enough
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.31,1:50:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我要像那些把行李搬上车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or I shall be like one of those guests who
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.14,1:50:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不肯走的客人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}pack the car and never leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.44,1:50:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mila-- Milady...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.77,1:50:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵吵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop that noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.15,1:50:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都听不到自己死去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't hear myself die.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.88,1:52:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也端过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take that as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.97,1:54:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  贝茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Bates.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.80,1:54:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我们来说是不寻常的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A strange day for you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.81,1:54:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于成了孤儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're orphans at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.02,1:54:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-早上好  -早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.24,1:54:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.32,1:54:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能来她会很高兴的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'd be so pleased you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.04,1:54:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得我第一次真切地看到她  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can remember the first time I really saw her, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.41,1:54:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近距离看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, close up, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.92,1:54:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时刚从门童升了职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd just been promoted from hallboy,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.04,1:54:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟当时的管家蒙乔伊先生在餐厅里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I was in the dining room with the old butler then, Mr. Mountjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.72,1:54:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很怕他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd been terrified of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.88,1:54:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她向我们走了过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then she walked towards us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.05,1:54:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当时在气什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was angry about something, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.14,1:54:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他都颤抖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I could see him tremble.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.89,1:54:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远没忘记那一幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never forgot that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.06,1:54:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后我就再不怕他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I was never afraid of him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.86,1:55:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我们家族历史的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You belong to our history.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.82,1:55:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  或许这段历史还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I wonder if your part is quite done.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.90,1:55:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意考虑回来工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you ever consider coming back?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.66,1:55:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少再工作一阵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a bit longer anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.95,1:55:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.20,1:55:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴罗要走了  我不能一个人调教一个新管家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barrow is leaving, and I can't break in a new butler alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.62,1:55:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让安德鲁在你的指导下准备接替你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could Andrew be your steady hand while you train him up to succeed you?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.50,1:55:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他能行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could he manage that, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.04,1:55:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.92,1:55:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假以时日的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In time.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.93,1:55:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫人的胸针\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her Ladyship's brooch.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.39,1:55:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐顿的火炬被传给您了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So now the Downton torch has passed to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.85,1:55:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是传给老爷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To His Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.89,1:55:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果我也要接过火炬  我要尽量骄傲地举起它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if I'm to carry it, too, I shall try to do so with pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.86,1:55:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能假装我没感到有些害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't pretend I'm not a little frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.78,1:55:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you have no need to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.45,1:55:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有这个力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have the strength for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.28,1:55:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.32,1:55:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有时会怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.03,1:55:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.29,1:55:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.58,1:56:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管重不重要  你永远可以指望我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you can always count on me, if that means anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.50,1:56:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我意义非凡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.30,1:56:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你是知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I think you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.26,1:56:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要单独待会儿再出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I just need a moment before we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.35,1:56:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.12,1:56:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did she have to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.62,1:56:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她希望我回来工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants me back in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.83,1:56:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做管家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.62,1:56:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does she indeed?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.84,1:56:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We ought to move off.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.96,1:56:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你组织了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for organizing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.01,1:56:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她留下了事无巨细的指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She left instructions down to the tiniest detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.84,1:56:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不难想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.09,1:56:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将来还要安葬我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be burying me one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.64,1:56:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴到时一切都会妥妥当当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'm glad to see it'll be done well.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.06,1:56:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose the point is
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.31,1:57:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡劳利家的人来来去去  但家族会一直传承\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}individual Crawleys come and go, but the family lives on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.19,1:57:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈知道也相信这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mama knew that and believed in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.56,1:57:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't she just.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.88,1:58:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走  我们进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way now. We shall go inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.95,1:59:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.24,1:59:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.25,1:59:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.58,1:59:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.38,1:59:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-恭喜  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.00,1:59:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.42,1:59:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.34,1:59:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜玻  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sybbie, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.35,1:59:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-恭喜  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.02,1:59:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的宝宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a bonny baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.40,1:59:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真帅气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's very handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.57,1:59:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  玛丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.19,1:59:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.40,1:59:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's this?
